WEBVTT

01:16.250 --> 01:20.166
<i>-[birds chirping]</i>
<i>-[rhythmic breaths]</i>

01:40.541 --> 01:46.500
<i>[radio in Spanish] </i>

01:46.583 --> 01:49.458
<i>[in Spanish] Irma will sleep at my mom's</i>
<i>so we can go to the movies.</i>

01:49.541 --> 01:52.458
<i>-</i>[man]<i> </i>Oh, okay.
-Don't be late.

01:52.916 --> 01:54.458
<i>Don't worry, I'll be there at six.</i>

01:54.916 --> 01:56.750
<i>[man shouting outside]</i>

01:57.875 --> 01:58.958
<i>Okay.</i>

01:59.041 --> 02:01.166
<i>-Not hungry?</i>
<i>-I'm running late.</i>

02:01.250 --> 02:03.375
<i>Give Daddy a hug.</i>

02:03.458 --> 02:04.750
<i>Her braid.</i>

02:05.291 --> 02:06.916
<i>[girl laughing]</i>

02:07.000 --> 02:09.333
<i>-Big kiss for Mommy.</i>
<i>-[man] Here, Mommy.</i>

02:10.000 --> 02:10.833
<i>[kissing]</i>

02:10.916 --> 02:12.708
<i>-Love you.</i>
<i>-Me too.</i>

02:12.791 --> 02:15.583
<i>Have a good day.</i>
<i>Wish Daddy a good day.</i>

02:16.291 --> 02:17.458
<i>-[kisses]</i>
<i>-[horn honks]</i>

02:23.083 --> 02:23.916
<i>[bus honks]</i>

02:25.666 --> 02:28.666
<i>[indistinct shouting]</i>

02:31.958 --> 02:33.166
<i>[indistinct radio]</i>

02:35.625 --> 02:40.375
<i>[radio grows louder]</i>

02:40.458 --> 02:42.208
<i>[radio static]</i>

02:42.583 --> 02:44.208
<i>[engine fires]</i>

02:59.166 --> 03:01.208
<i>-Ready?</i>
<i>-Ready.</i>

03:01.583 --> 03:02.750
<i>Go.</i>

03:02.833 --> 03:04.250
<i>[wind whistles]</i>

03:07.333 --> 03:08.208
<i>[wind whistles]</i>

03:18.375 --> 03:19.541
<i>Coming to lunch?</i>

03:19.958 --> 03:21.291
<i>Meet you there.</i>

03:33.958 --> 03:38.125
<i>[staticky voice from radio]</i>

03:38.500 --> 03:41.791
<i>[another voice from radio]</i>

03:41.875 --> 03:43.041
<i>-[radio feedback]</i>
<i>-[cable clatters]</i>

03:43.333 --> 03:45.666
<i>[radio signal clicking]</i>

03:45.750 --> 03:47.833
<i>[feedback fades to a buzz]</i>

04:11.541 --> 04:18.375
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

04:39.416 --> 04:41.791
<i>Are you Olga Salanueva,</i>
<i>René González's wife?</i>

04:43.166 --> 04:45.125
<i>Did something happen?</i>

04:45.208 --> 04:47.000
<i>We're from the Ministry of the Interior.</i>

04:47.541 --> 04:49.916
<i>He had an accident?</i>
<i>Is he alive?</i>

04:50.000 --> 04:51.916
<i>He's alive, not hurt.</i>

04:55.208 --> 04:58.250
<i>Comrade Salanueva,</i>
<i>your husband is in Florida.</i>

04:59.416 --> 05:00.500
<i>He defected.</i>

05:00.583 --> 05:02.125
<i>He stole a plane,</i>

05:02.208 --> 05:06.250
<i>flew under our radar,</i>
<i>landed at a U.S. airbase in Miami.</i>

05:07.291 --> 05:09.291
<i>[camera shutters clicking]</i>

05:14.583 --> 05:17.291
<i>[in English] Had you been planning this</i>
<i>for some time, sir?</i>

05:17.750 --> 05:19.875
<i>The escape took me</i>
<i>three months to prepare.</i>

05:20.250 --> 05:21.416
<i>To--to plan.</i>

05:22.416 --> 05:25.166
<i>But I had already said goodbye to Cuba</i>
<i>many years ago.</i>

05:25.250 --> 05:26.666
<i>Why did you defect?</i>

05:26.750 --> 05:28.666
<i>In Cuba, everything's short.</i>

05:29.375 --> 05:31.291
<i>Electricity. Food.</i>

05:32.666 --> 05:33.500
<i>Everything.</i>

05:35.041 --> 05:37.583
<i>Potato, rice, even sugar...</i>

05:38.625 --> 05:39.458
<i>is rationed.</i>

05:41.083 --> 05:43.541
<i>Every drop of fuel for our airplanes</i>
<i>is counted.</i>

05:43.625 --> 05:44.875
<i>I'm a pilot.</i>

05:45.750 --> 05:47.708
<i>I don't want to go on living like that.</i>

05:47.958 --> 05:51.208
<i>Does it mean</i>
<i>you will be applying for political asylum?</i>

05:51.416 --> 05:52.666
<i>I don't need to.</i>

05:53.166 --> 05:54.625
<i>I was born in Chicago.</i>

05:55.375 --> 05:57.833
<i>So I'm an American citizen</i>
<i>and I'm very proud of it.</i>

05:58.750 --> 06:02.166
<i>[in Spanish] If you receive</i>
<i>the slightest information,</i>

06:02.250 --> 06:05.500
<i>it is your duty</i>
<i>to inform us immediately.</i>

06:05.583 --> 06:07.541
<i>You can count on it.</i>

06:09.666 --> 06:10.500
<i>[sighs]</i>

06:15.958 --> 06:19.333
<i>[dialing numbers]</i>

06:19.416 --> 06:22.208
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

06:22.291 --> 06:23.125
<i>[line connects]</i>

06:23.208 --> 06:24.041
<i>[man] </i>Hello.

06:24.125 --> 06:25.250
<i>Roberto,</i>

06:25.875 --> 06:27.666
<i>you heard about your brother?</i>

06:27.750 --> 06:28.916
<i>Listen--</i>

06:29.291 --> 06:32.083
<i>I need your help</i>
<i>getting through this.</i>

06:32.166 --> 06:33.666
<i>I'll come over later.</i>

06:34.083 --> 06:36.166
<i>I'll tell our parents first.</i>

06:36.250 --> 06:37.083
<i>Okay.</i>

06:37.625 --> 06:39.583
<i>Then we'll tell Irma.</i>

06:39.916 --> 06:43.333
<i>It'll be hard for her to understand</i>
<i>why he abandoned her.</i>

06:43.416 --> 06:46.375
<i>But I'll be there with you. Okay?</i>

06:46.791 --> 06:48.375
<i>I'll help you.</i>

06:48.833 --> 06:52.750
<i>[melancholic music playing]</i>

06:52.833 --> 06:56.541
<i>[sirens blaring]</i>

06:57.250 --> 06:58.875
<i>[man] </i>René, your new home.

06:59.833 --> 07:01.750
<i>-Thanks.</i>
<i>-You're welcome.</i>

07:04.375 --> 07:08.666
<i>[man] Rent is paid. Three months</i>
<i>should give you time to get settled.</i>

07:09.791 --> 07:14.166
<i>[man] It's basic, but don't worry.</i>
<i>We'll help you get more stuff.</i>

07:16.041 --> 07:17.958
<i>Who should I thank?</i>

07:18.041 --> 07:19.250
<i>[man] The CANF.</i>

07:19.916 --> 07:22.541
<i>Cuban American National Foundation.</i>

07:23.666 --> 07:25.125
<i>Jorge Mas Canosa.</i>

07:25.208 --> 07:26.791
<i>[man] Our president.</i>

07:27.958 --> 07:29.791
<i>[man] He will rebuild Cuba.</i>

07:30.375 --> 07:34.583
<i>Anything you need</i>
<i>for your work, your family,</i>

07:35.375 --> 07:36.208
<i>ask him.</i>

07:36.291 --> 07:38.583
<i>You start tomorrow,</i>
<i>Opa-locka airport.</i>

07:38.666 --> 07:40.041
<i>As a flight instructor.</i>

07:40.125 --> 07:43.375
<i>Pay's not great,</i>
<i>but you can earn extra on the side.</i>

07:43.750 --> 07:47.833
<i>[melancholic music continues]</i>

07:56.583 --> 07:58.208
<i>[sighs]</i>

08:09.458 --> 08:10.416
<i>[engine running]</i>

08:18.125 --> 08:19.833
<i>[in English] So you think I'm ready</i>
<i>for my first solo?</i>

08:19.916 --> 08:21.541
<i>Not yet, we need to work on your landing.</i>

08:21.625 --> 08:23.666
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-We try it again next week, okay?</i>

08:31.583 --> 08:35.416
<i>[in Spanish] May I sit with you?</i>
<i>Let me introduce myself.</i>

08:35.500 --> 08:36.958
<i>No need.</i>

08:37.791 --> 08:39.166
<i>You're José Basulto.</i>

08:39.916 --> 08:41.208
<i>At your service.</i>

08:41.625 --> 08:44.166
<i>"Arch-enemy of the Cuban Revolution."</i>

08:44.250 --> 08:47.708
<i>For me, that's a badge of honor.</i>

08:48.208 --> 08:50.041
<i>[Basulto] You fought in Angola.</i>

08:50.125 --> 08:51.583
<i>Tank commander.</i>

08:52.375 --> 08:54.458
<i>Two years in the jungle.</i>
<i>54 missions.</i>

08:56.416 --> 08:58.625
<i>Good reasons for us to get along.</i>

08:59.166 --> 09:00.083
<i>Why?</i>

09:00.208 --> 09:02.666
<i>We need men like you.</i>

09:03.708 --> 09:05.041
<i>I'm not a politician.</i>

09:07.541 --> 09:10.000
<i>[Basulto] Ever hear</i>
<i>of Gregorio Pérez Ricardo?</i>

09:10.500 --> 09:14.458
<i>The kid was 15</i>
<i>when he fled Cuba on a raft.</i>

09:15.208 --> 09:17.333
<i>But he wasn't as lucky as you.</i>

09:18.541 --> 09:20.666
<i>The U.S. Coast Guard found him</i>

09:20.750 --> 09:24.291
<i>so dehydrated,</i>
<i>they couldn't revive him.</i>

09:25.250 --> 09:27.916
<i>So we set up an organization</i>

09:28.000 --> 09:30.541
<i>called "Brothers to the Rescue",</i>

09:31.333 --> 09:33.833
<i>to help our brothers.</i>

09:33.916 --> 09:36.791
<i>So nothing like that ever happens again.</i>

09:38.458 --> 09:39.875
<i>How do you plan to do that?</i>

09:41.000 --> 09:42.625
<i>Eriberto, a coffee.</i>

09:42.708 --> 09:44.083
<i>Want one?</i>

09:44.166 --> 09:45.208
<i>Sure.</i>

09:45.291 --> 09:46.333
<i>Two.</i>

09:49.041 --> 09:50.541
<i>You know that</i>

09:50.625 --> 09:52.625
<i>I used to be a violent man.</i>

09:53.291 --> 09:56.416
<i>Trained by the U.S. as a terrorist.</i>

09:56.791 --> 09:58.791
<i>My hero was John Wayne.</i>

10:00.083 --> 10:01.291
<i>But not anymore.</i>

10:02.333 --> 10:04.416
<i>Now I'm a kind of...</i>

10:05.333 --> 10:06.416
<i>Jedi.</i>

10:07.416 --> 10:09.041
<i>Like Luke Skywalker.</i>

10:10.000 --> 10:11.750
<i>The Force is with us.</i>

10:12.166 --> 10:13.375
<i>Understand?</i>

10:13.833 --> 10:14.791
<i>Sort of.</i>

10:15.208 --> 10:18.833
<i>It's all about solidarity, humanism.</i>

10:18.916 --> 10:23.375
<i>We'll go find rafters in the sea</i>

10:23.458 --> 10:25.833
<i>and guide them to freedom.</i>

10:27.541 --> 10:28.375
<i>Thank you.</i>

10:31.666 --> 10:33.000
<i>By monitoring the ocean.</i>

10:33.625 --> 10:35.416
<i>[Basulto] We have the planes</i>

10:35.500 --> 10:38.750
<i>but we don't have</i>
<i>enough pilots like you.</i>

10:41.541 --> 10:45.291
<i>It's $25 a run,</i>
<i>plus 25 per flight hour.</i>

10:45.375 --> 10:46.750
<i>Who pays?</i>

10:46.833 --> 10:50.833
<i>[Basulto] Jorge Mas Canosa.</i>
<i>Money is not a problem for him.</i>

10:52.625 --> 10:57.708
<i>The collapse of the Soviet Union</i>
<i>has raised people's hopes.</i>

10:57.791 --> 10:59.083
<i>And yet...</i>

10:59.791 --> 11:01.041
<i>Castro is holding on.</i>

11:01.125 --> 11:03.708
<i>Without Russian money,</i>
<i>he won't last long.</i>

11:04.125 --> 11:06.208
<i>When the regime collapses,</i>

11:06.291 --> 11:11.000
<i>they'll have to return the refineries,</i>
<i>banks, factories. And casinos!</i>

11:12.416 --> 11:16.916
<i>The stakes are enormous for every exile.</i>

11:17.000 --> 11:18.250
<i>Take yourself.</i>

11:18.708 --> 11:20.625
<i>You left your family there.</i>

11:20.708 --> 11:24.291
<i>You're a brave man. You fled communism.</i>

11:24.833 --> 11:27.750
<i>You started over here in Miami.</i>

11:29.583 --> 11:30.416
<i>But...</i>

11:33.375 --> 11:35.083
<i>you have a choice to make.</i>

11:36.333 --> 11:37.875
<i>Keep on gardening...</i>

11:39.708 --> 11:43.416
<i>or help bring democracy</i>
<i>to our country.</i>

11:44.583 --> 11:50.666
<i>[intensifying engine whir]</i>

11:50.750 --> 11:52.625
<i>[voices crying out]</i>

11:52.708 --> 11:57.583
<i>[René in English over radio]</i>
November 2-5-0-6 to base.

11:57.666 --> 12:03.208
<i>Two rafts spotted at 24-53 by 81-42,</i>
<i>drifting north/north-east.</i>

12:03.291 --> 12:07.125
<i>About 20 people aboard.</i>
<i>I repeat, 20 people aboard.</i>

12:07.666 --> 12:10.541
<i>-[people shouting]</i>
<i>-[plane engine grows louder]</i>

12:11.208 --> 12:13.375
<i>[René] </i>Dropping now, I repeat,
dropping now.

12:14.666 --> 12:16.625
<i>-[shouts continue]</i>
<i>-[René] </i>Dropping now.

12:17.625 --> 12:18.916
<i>-[loud splash]</i>
<i>-[all shouting]</i>

12:19.000 --> 12:23.083
<i>-[loud splash]</i>
<i>-[shouting continues]</i>

12:32.583 --> 12:33.958
<i>[in Spanish] You saved them.</i>

12:34.791 --> 12:36.625
<i>Coast Guard on the way!</i>

12:36.708 --> 12:38.541
<i>-Those poor people.</i>
<i>-Good job.</i>

12:38.625 --> 12:39.958
<i>I hope they make it.</i>

12:40.041 --> 12:42.041
<i>Sure they will. Look...</i>

12:42.416 --> 12:45.458
<i>Hey, a gift from Willy Chirino.</i>

12:45.541 --> 12:46.875
<i>Really?</i>

12:47.458 --> 12:49.000
<i>[Basulto] And that one...</i>

12:49.083 --> 12:50.583
<i>Gloria Estefan.</i>

12:50.666 --> 12:53.291
<i>Damn!</i>
<i>Ask her to come christen it.</i>

12:53.375 --> 12:55.500
<i>Good idea</i>
<i>but don't get your hopes up.</i>

12:55.583 --> 12:56.416
<i>[René laughs]</i>

13:01.500 --> 13:03.583
<i>[René in Spanish over radio] </i>
What are you doing?

13:03.666 --> 13:05.500
<i>We're crossing Parallel 24.</i>

13:05.583 --> 13:07.833
<i>Entering Cuban airspace.</i>

13:08.166 --> 13:09.416
<i>Listen.</i>

13:09.500 --> 13:12.458
<i>We're not just</i>
<i>a humanitarian organization.</i>

13:12.541 --> 13:15.625
<i>We're a militant organization.</i>

13:15.708 --> 13:18.416
<i>[in English] </i>Good afternoon, Havana.
This is November 2-5-0-6. 

13:18.500 --> 13:21.958
<i>We are crossing Parallel 24.</i>
<i>Today, our operations will be</i>

13:22.041 --> 13:23.875
<i>-in the northern part of Havana.</i>
-[radio static]

13:24.416 --> 13:28.583
<i>[man on radio] </i>Received, but I inform you
that the area north of Havana is active.

13:28.666 --> 13:30.458
<i>You will be at risk.</i>

13:30.541 --> 13:32.833
<i>Copy. We are aware of the risk.</i>

13:33.166 --> 13:36.583
<i>But, as free Cubans,</i>
<i>we are prepared to take it.</i>

13:47.458 --> 13:50.208
<i>[jet engine approaches and zooms past]</i>

13:53.666 --> 13:55.208
<i>[in Spanish] </i>They're showing off.

13:55.291 --> 13:56.958
<i>Showing off, my ass.</i>

13:57.041 --> 13:57.958
<i>[laughs]</i>

13:58.041 --> 14:05.041
<i>[Spanish guitar music playing]</i>

14:08.750 --> 14:10.208
<i>[Basulto] </i>Take over.

14:10.625 --> 14:12.708
<i>Follow the </i>Malecon.

14:17.041 --> 14:18.375
<i>[Basulto] </i>Turn right.

14:25.125 --> 14:28.000
<i>[paper flapping in air]</i>

14:32.875 --> 14:34.291
<i>[all shouting and screaming]</i>

14:38.541 --> 14:40.750
<i>COMRADES NO!</i>
<i>BROTHERS!</i>

14:52.333 --> 14:53.625
<i>[René in voiceover] </i>Dear Olga,

14:55.250 --> 14:57.791
<i>You haven't answered my letters.</i>

14:58.583 --> 15:00.041
<i>I understand your reasons.</i>

15:01.000 --> 15:02.791
<i>But understand mine.</i>

15:04.500 --> 15:05.666
<i>I'm a pilot.</i>

15:06.375 --> 15:09.166
<i>I don't want to be</i>
<i>a flight instructor all my life.</i>

15:09.541 --> 15:11.166
<i>It's always tough at first</i>

15:12.375 --> 15:15.000
<i>but this is a land of opportunities.</i>

15:15.500 --> 15:17.416
<i>There are plenty for all of us.</i>

15:19.041 --> 15:21.416
<i>I'm checking out schools for Irma.</i>

15:24.041 --> 15:25.416
<i>[Olga in voiceover] </i>Dear René,

15:26.416 --> 15:28.583
<i>I've received your many letters.</i>

15:29.041 --> 15:32.375
<i>I'm so saddened by this,</i>
<i>I can't open them.</i>

15:33.833 --> 15:35.833
<i>Here, life is very difficult.</i>

15:35.916 --> 15:39.875
<i>Blackouts last eight hours,</i>
<i>and it's difficult to find food.</i>

15:40.416 --> 15:43.291
<i>It's harder and harder</i>
<i>to get by on my own.</i>

15:44.041 --> 15:45.916
<i>Irma is a big girl now.</i>

15:46.000 --> 15:49.208
<i>She's asking questions.</i>
<i>I hate lying to her.</i>

15:50.041 --> 15:52.666
<i>I don't want her to learn</i>
<i>her father's a traitor.</i>

15:52.958 --> 15:55.833
<i>Believe it or not,</i>
<i>last week we got robbed.</i>

15:55.916 --> 15:58.458
<i>They took all our valuables.</i>

15:59.541 --> 16:02.250
<i>But I'm a fighter, you know that.</i>

16:02.916 --> 16:05.708
<i>You also know I'm not angry with you.</i>

16:06.250 --> 16:09.375
<i>I wish you luck in your new life.</i>

16:10.375 --> 16:11.916
<i>But I regret to tell you,</i>

16:12.666 --> 16:14.041
<i>it won't be with me.</i>

16:27.416 --> 16:32.208
<i>[children playing]</i>

16:35.125 --> 16:38.333
<i>[birds chirping]</i>

16:40.708 --> 16:46.250
<i>[engine approaches and recedes]</i>

17:04.666 --> 17:09.250
<i>[breathing with effort]</i>

17:16.583 --> 17:18.583
<i>[deep breaths]</i>

17:19.250 --> 17:20.166
<i>[gasps]</i>

17:27.250 --> 17:32.083
<i>[heavy breathing]</i>

17:32.166 --> 17:35.458
<i>[bubbling water]</i>

17:37.000 --> 17:39.000
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

17:51.000 --> 17:55.708
<i>[gasping]</i>

18:04.791 --> 18:05.750
<i>[soldier in English] Freeze!</i>

18:05.833 --> 18:08.000
<i>-Don't shoot!</i>
<i>-[siren wails]</i>

18:08.416 --> 18:10.333
<i>-[rifle loads]</i>
<i>-I am a Cuban officer!</i>

18:10.416 --> 18:13.583
<i>-I am defecting!</i>
<i>-[dogs barking]</i>

18:15.583 --> 18:18.250
<i>[man] My military I.D. My pilot's log.</i>

18:27.000 --> 18:28.458
<i>[American officer] Who's this guy?</i>

18:28.541 --> 18:29.583
<i>He's my friend.</i>

18:31.250 --> 18:32.958
<i>Arnaldo Ochoa.</i>

18:34.416 --> 18:36.750
<i>Hero of the Cuban Revolution.</i>

18:38.083 --> 18:40.333
<i>Hero of the war in Angola.</i>

18:41.458 --> 18:44.166
<i>He was arrested and executed.</i>

18:44.250 --> 18:45.708
<i>For drug smuggling.</i>

18:45.791 --> 18:47.791
<i>An associate of Pablo Escobar also.</i>

18:47.875 --> 18:52.708
<i>No. That's what the regime says</i>
<i>when they want to get rid of an opponent.</i>

18:57.375 --> 18:58.416
<i>Thank you.</i>

19:03.583 --> 19:05.041
<i>[moans, laughs]</i>

19:05.833 --> 19:06.666
<i>Eat up.</i>

19:07.208 --> 19:10.375
<i>For someone who's been eating</i>
<i>McCastro's for years...</i>

19:10.458 --> 19:11.875
<i>[laughs]</i>

19:11.958 --> 19:14.750
<i>McDonald's is a delicacy.</i>

19:15.708 --> 19:16.583
<i>Come on, why now?</i>

19:17.375 --> 19:20.208
<i>General Ochoa was executed</i>
<i>three years ago.</i>

19:21.125 --> 19:24.416
<i>I didn't think the regime would survive</i>
<i>the end of the Soviet Union.</i>

19:26.166 --> 19:27.791
<i>[inhales] And it did.</i>

19:29.083 --> 19:34.000
<i>[sighs] But then my brothers,</i>
<i>Alejandro and Raúl, also fighter pilots,</i>

19:35.000 --> 19:37.666
<i>they were less patient than me.</i>
<i>They tried to run away</i>

19:37.916 --> 19:40.250
<i>but got arrested and imprisoned.</i>

19:40.333 --> 19:41.916
<i>Do you have any family?</i>

19:42.000 --> 19:42.958
<i>Any children?</i>

19:43.333 --> 19:46.291
<i>[sniffs] My wife, Amelia,</i>
<i>and two children.</i>

19:46.375 --> 19:48.000
<i>Will they be joining you in the States?</i>

19:49.541 --> 19:51.000
<i>We are divorced.</i>

19:52.000 --> 19:54.000
<i>And she has custody of the children.</i>

19:55.041 --> 19:58.125
<i>[PA in English] </i>May I have your attention,
please. This is the final boarding call...

19:58.208 --> 20:02.708
<i>[men speaking indistinctly]</i>

20:03.041 --> 20:05.250
<i>[in Spanish] The couch</i>
<i>is the best I can do.</i>

20:05.333 --> 20:08.166
<i>-Don't worry about it.</i>
<i>-It'll help for a while.</i>

20:08.250 --> 20:10.083
<i>It's perfect, thanks.</i>

20:10.166 --> 20:15.333
<i>[upbeat music playing]</i>

20:20.958 --> 20:21.875
<i>Listen...</i>

20:23.250 --> 20:25.750
<i>We have associations</i>
<i>that help defectors.</i>

20:25.833 --> 20:27.625
<i>But let me ask you something.</i>

20:27.791 --> 20:28.958
<i>Why did you come?</i>

20:29.416 --> 20:31.708
<i>To deliver pizzas or to strike it rich?</i>

20:32.333 --> 20:33.625
<i>-What about you?</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

20:34.250 --> 20:35.250
<i>Me?</i>

20:36.458 --> 20:38.166
<i>I'm a </i>biznero, <i>dude.</i>

20:38.250 --> 20:40.791
<i>You know me.</i>
<i>A little bit of everything.</i>

20:42.083 --> 20:43.333
<i>And that's enough?</i>

20:44.166 --> 20:45.875
<i>[in English] No way, man.</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

20:45.958 --> 20:47.416
<i>[in Spanish] What do you think?</i>

20:48.125 --> 20:49.166
<i>So?</i>

20:49.500 --> 20:50.708
<i>Should I tell you?</i>

20:52.083 --> 20:54.250
<i>I'm also an FBI informer.</i>

20:56.125 --> 20:59.125
<i>I update them</i>
<i>on the community's mood.</i>

21:00.416 --> 21:02.375
<i>And the pay is good.</i>

21:03.291 --> 21:04.500
<i>Big money!</i>

21:06.958 --> 21:08.708
<i>[singing in Spanish]</i>

21:11.166 --> 21:18.166
<i>[both singing]</i>

21:19.500 --> 21:21.416
<i>Thank you for the mass.</i>
<i>Really good. Thank you.</i>

21:24.666 --> 21:27.083
<i>-Ana, hey!</i>
<i>-[laughing] No!</i>

21:27.166 --> 21:28.708
<i>-[in English] How are you?</i>
<i>-I'm good.</i>

21:28.791 --> 21:31.000
<i>-It's been a long time. I can't believe it</i>
<i>-Oh, my God. How have you been?</i>

21:31.083 --> 21:33.291
<i>-I've been good. You look great!</i>
<i>-The family, good?</i>

21:33.375 --> 21:35.250
<i>You know what?</i>
<i>Let me introduce you to somebody.</i>

21:35.333 --> 21:36.500
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-Come here.</i>

21:36.583 --> 21:38.458
<i>[in Spanish] Cousin, come here.</i>

21:39.208 --> 21:41.208
<i>[in English] This is my cousin,</i>
<i>Juan Pablo Roque.</i>

21:41.291 --> 21:44.166
<i>-Very nice meeting you.</i>
<i>-[Ana] Hi. Nice meeting you.</i>

21:44.250 --> 21:47.041
<i>You're the officer who swam</i>
<i>to the U.S. base.</i>

21:47.125 --> 21:48.583
<i>Yeah, that's me.</i>

21:49.750 --> 21:52.333
<i>I know Guantanamo Bay.</i>
<i>You're not afraid of sharks?</i>

21:53.250 --> 21:54.625
<i>Sharks, uh...</i>

21:55.541 --> 21:56.541
<i>I was lucky.</i>

21:57.500 --> 21:58.333
<i>[laughs]</i>

22:01.958 --> 22:04.333
<i>Did anyone tell you</i>
<i>you look like a movie star?</i>

22:04.708 --> 22:07.208
<i>-Well, I am a movie star.</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

22:07.291 --> 22:11.750
<i>Or I like to think that I'm sexier</i>
<i>than a movie star, actually.</i>

22:11.833 --> 22:14.041
<i>[Ana laughs]</i>

22:17.708 --> 22:18.666
<i>[Ana] Thank you.</i>

22:19.375 --> 22:20.875
<i>That was a lovely evening.</i>

22:21.791 --> 22:25.291
<i>Was it lovely because you...</i>
<i>liked the movie?</i>

22:25.375 --> 22:26.250
<i>[laughs]</i>

22:26.333 --> 22:29.500
<i>[sighs] Not only.</i>

22:29.583 --> 22:33.208
<i>So... so I think</i>
<i>we will see each other again.</i>

22:35.375 --> 22:36.625
<i>[door softly opens]</i>

22:37.125 --> 22:38.125
<i>[whispering] Wait.</i>

22:38.208 --> 22:40.916
<i>[gasps] No.</i>

22:41.000 --> 22:43.166
<i>-[softly] Why?</i>
<i>-[firm] Because I have to go. I--</i>

22:43.250 --> 22:44.083
<i>[sighs]</i>

22:44.916 --> 22:47.291
<i>I don't want my ex-husband to see us.</i>

22:48.208 --> 22:50.083
<i>Your ex-husband?</i>

22:50.166 --> 22:53.916
<i>Yes. He's moving out.</i>
<i>But his apartment is being renovated.</i>

22:54.000 --> 22:56.166
<i>So, he's staying with me in the meantime.</i>

22:56.250 --> 22:58.250
<i>Is it over between you?</i>

22:58.333 --> 22:59.916
<i>-Yes!</i>
<i>-So?</i>

23:00.000 --> 23:00.833
<i>I just...</i>

23:01.916 --> 23:03.916
<i>I'm afraid of him. He's violent.</i>

23:04.666 --> 23:05.666
<i>I'll protect you.</i>

23:06.208 --> 23:09.750
<i>[laughs]</i>
<i>You'll be my bodyguard?</i>

23:09.833 --> 23:13.458
<i>-Yes. Like in the movie tonight.</i>
<i>-Like Kevin Costner for Whitney Houston?</i>

23:13.541 --> 23:14.500
<i>-Yeah.</i>
<i>-Oh, God.</i>

23:17.541 --> 23:18.833
<i>[both moaning]</i>

23:19.500 --> 23:20.333
<i>[Ana groans]</i>

23:21.458 --> 23:23.166
<i>[whispering] I'm gonna go.</i>

23:25.458 --> 23:27.541
<i>We'll meet again.</i>
<i>[firm] We'll meet again!</i>

23:29.500 --> 23:30.333
<i>[door slams]</i>

23:30.416 --> 23:32.458
<i>[in Spanish] You're a friend</i>
<i>of Nico Gutiérrez's?</i>

23:32.541 --> 23:34.416
<i>His personal trainer.</i>

23:34.500 --> 23:35.458
<i>Great!</i>

23:35.541 --> 23:37.500
<i>Well, Nico...</i>

23:38.166 --> 23:39.416
<i>suggested I call you.</i>

23:39.500 --> 23:43.375
<i>He's working out.</i>
<i>I've told him to for ages.</i>

23:44.166 --> 23:45.500
<i>Look, Basulto.</i>

23:47.166 --> 23:49.166
<i>[Basulto] Your pilot's log.</i>

23:51.958 --> 23:53.541
<i>I was a major in the Air Force.</i>

23:56.916 --> 23:58.541
<i>I used to fly MiGs.</i>

23:59.541 --> 24:01.541
<i>[Basulto] You're more experienced than me.</i>

24:02.458 --> 24:04.250
<i>Want to fly again?</i>

24:04.333 --> 24:05.625
<i>I left Cuba...</i>

24:06.333 --> 24:08.250
<i>to fight the Castros.</i>

24:09.875 --> 24:14.125
<i>In our organization,</i>
<i>there's an elite group.</i>

24:14.708 --> 24:16.666
<i>We call them the kamikazes.</i>

24:18.208 --> 24:20.500
<i>I'd like to know what it's about.</i>

24:20.583 --> 24:22.500
<i>We don't respect safety rules</i>

24:22.583 --> 24:24.708
<i>or the laws of aeronautics.</i>

24:24.791 --> 24:26.291
<i>Meaning?</i>

24:26.541 --> 24:28.166
<i>If you join us,</i>

24:28.250 --> 24:30.458
<i>you'll be flying 9-hour days,</i>

24:30.541 --> 24:34.250
<i>7 days a week, every month, no breaks.</i>

24:34.333 --> 24:35.166
<i>[in English] Full time.</i>

24:37.416 --> 24:39.500
<i>[in Spanish] My friend...</i>

24:41.083 --> 24:42.041
<i>That's illegal.</i>

24:42.541 --> 24:44.166
<i>[laughs] Illegal...</i>

24:44.291 --> 24:45.541
<i>And very dangerous.</i>

24:45.625 --> 24:47.583
<i>You're telling me!</i>

24:47.666 --> 24:49.166
<i>I had a fire aboard.</i>

24:49.708 --> 24:53.625
<i>Made a landing on Cayo Sal,</i>
<i>off Venezuela.</i>

24:53.958 --> 24:55.708
<i>Man, was I in deep shit!</i>

24:56.666 --> 24:59.583
<i>Truth is, Juan Pablo Roque,</i>

24:59.666 --> 25:02.208
<i>we at Brothers to the Rescue</i>

25:03.000 --> 25:05.833
<i>need pilots like you.</i>

25:12.583 --> 25:14.250
<i>[signal beeping]</i>

25:15.541 --> 25:18.208
<i>[over radio in English]</i>
November 58 Bravo-Bravo<i> </i>to base.

25:18.333 --> 25:24.541
<i>Cuban Coastguard spotted</i> <i>at 23-80 by 81-77</i>
<i>heading north/north-west.</i>

25:24.625 --> 25:27.125
<i>Bravo-Bravo to base.</i>
<i>Cuban Coastguard spotted...</i>

25:27.208 --> 25:30.000
<i>[in Spanish] Cuban Coast Guard ahead.</i>
<i>Change course.</i>

25:30.541 --> 25:32.708
<i>South-southeast. Varadero.</i>

25:41.166 --> 25:44.541
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

25:44.666 --> 25:45.500
<i>Hey.</i>

25:47.166 --> 25:49.416
<i>-How did it go?</i>
<i>-Things went wrong.</i>

25:50.500 --> 25:52.208
<i>-Nabbed by the Cubans?</i>
<i>-[René] Mm-mm.</i>

25:53.000 --> 25:56.750
<i>They changed course.</i>
<i>Their engine broke down off Varadero.</i>

25:57.208 --> 26:00.750
<i>U.S. Customs found them.</i>
<i>Seized their weapons.</i>

26:00.833 --> 26:01.791
<i>Shit!</i>

26:02.750 --> 26:04.041
<i>Hope they don't talk.</i>

26:04.125 --> 26:05.125
<i>[René] Mm-hmm.</i>

26:05.208 --> 26:07.125
<i>No one must know we guided them.</i>

26:09.541 --> 26:10.958
<i>Your family stayed in Cuba?</i>

26:11.375 --> 26:12.208
<i>Yes.</i>

26:13.958 --> 26:15.958
<i>Life is tough there, as you know.</i>

26:17.958 --> 26:19.958
<i>Their connection to me</i>

26:20.708 --> 26:23.291
<i>doesn't make things easier.</i>

26:23.583 --> 26:24.916
<i>It complicates everything.</i>

26:25.916 --> 26:27.916
<i>For them, I'm a traitor.</i>

26:28.541 --> 26:29.375
<i>A </i>gusano.

26:30.541 --> 26:33.000
<i>Sure your wife still loves you?</i>

26:33.083 --> 26:35.041
<i>[René] I'm still in love with her.</i>

26:35.500 --> 26:37.625
<i>I can't live without that woman.</i>

26:39.708 --> 26:41.583
<i>And I think she misses me.</i>

26:41.666 --> 26:42.958
<i>So does my daughter.</i>

26:44.250 --> 26:45.625
<i>I want to believe that.</i>

26:47.125 --> 26:48.000
<i>What about you?</i>

26:48.416 --> 26:51.791
<i>You're a star here, you're on TV and all.</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

26:52.833 --> 26:54.166
<i>Dude,</i>

26:55.625 --> 26:57.375
<i>if I were a star,</i>

26:57.458 --> 26:59.708
<i>I wouldn't be on this bus with you.</i>

27:00.208 --> 27:02.583
<i>I'd be in a limousine.</i>

27:04.083 --> 27:05.125
<i>You know what?</i>

27:05.833 --> 27:09.333
<i>A paparazzi offered me 5,000</i>

27:10.541 --> 27:13.708
<i>for pictures of me at the beach</i>
<i>with girls in bikinis.</i>

27:15.916 --> 27:17.041
<i>What did you tell him?</i>

27:17.708 --> 27:18.583
<i>Nothing.</i>

27:20.875 --> 27:21.708
<i>I...</i>

27:23.166 --> 27:25.125
<i>I'm starting my life over,</i>

27:25.791 --> 27:26.916
<i>but not like that.</i>

27:29.083 --> 27:30.083
<i>[René] I get it.</i>

27:33.708 --> 27:35.625
<i>I'm marrying Ana Margarita.</i>

27:36.125 --> 27:37.375
<i>No way.</i>

27:38.250 --> 27:39.916
<i>Good going, brother.</i>

27:47.333 --> 27:50.416
<i>[reversing vehicle beeping]</i>

27:52.458 --> 27:55.291
<i>[indistinct conversations]</i>

28:19.708 --> 28:20.750
<i>[man] Olga.</i>

28:23.083 --> 28:23.958
<i>Olga.</i>

28:28.916 --> 28:30.541
<i>[Olga] How did it go?</i>

28:31.583 --> 28:33.458
<i>-[Olga] Did you eat well?</i>
<i>-[Irma] Yes.</i>

28:34.000 --> 28:35.500
<i>[Roberto] A fight with her cousin.</i>

28:35.583 --> 28:36.875
<i>I bit him.</i>

28:36.958 --> 28:38.750
<i>Why did you bite him?</i>

28:38.833 --> 28:40.625
<i>I'm not saying.</i>

28:40.708 --> 28:43.416
<i>Go wash and straight to bed.</i>

28:43.500 --> 28:45.041
<i>Look at the time.</i>

28:46.125 --> 28:49.333
<i>Psst, hey!</i>
<i>No goodnight kiss for Uncle?</i>

28:49.416 --> 28:50.250
<i>Come here.</i>

28:51.083 --> 28:53.458
<i>[sighs, kisses]</i>

28:53.541 --> 28:54.500
<i>See you tomorrow.</i>

28:54.583 --> 28:56.458
<i>Goodnight, Uncle Roberto.</i>

28:56.541 --> 28:58.083
<i>Goodnight, miss.</i>

29:01.291 --> 29:04.500
<i>There are bags of his clothes</i>
<i>in the bedroom.</i>

29:05.083 --> 29:06.833
<i>[Roberto] I'll give some to our father.</i>

29:07.125 --> 29:09.250
<i>As long as you get rid of them.</i>

29:10.000 --> 29:12.583
<i>I want nothing of René's here.</i>

29:16.083 --> 29:18.708
<i>[Olga] Now tell me</i>
<i>why you bit your cousin.</i>

29:18.916 --> 29:20.583
<i>We played Memory.</i>

29:20.666 --> 29:22.125
<i>I won all 10 rounds.</i>

29:22.208 --> 29:24.500
<i>[Irma] I told him I was the champ.</i>

29:24.583 --> 29:27.000
<i>Always bragging.</i>

29:27.083 --> 29:29.666
<i>He said I was the champ,</i>

29:30.041 --> 29:32.208
<i>but my father is a traitor.</i>

29:32.583 --> 29:33.416
<i>[sighs]</i>

29:33.500 --> 29:35.375
<i>You should have explained.</i>

29:35.833 --> 29:38.208
<i>Is it true Daddy's a traitor?</i>

29:39.083 --> 29:40.333
<i>My sweetheart,</i>

29:40.875 --> 29:45.791
<i>I've often told you</i>
<i>why Daddy went abroad.</i>

29:46.541 --> 29:50.625
<i>To do business</i>
<i>to help our country's economy.</i>

29:50.708 --> 29:53.000
<i>Fighting the U.S. embargo.</i>

29:53.083 --> 29:55.083
<i>That's not being a traitor.</i>

29:55.166 --> 29:57.375
<i>That's being a patriot.</i>

29:58.583 --> 30:00.083
<i>-[Olga] Come here.</i>
<i>-[Irma sniffs]</i>

30:00.166 --> 30:02.875
<i>[Olga sighs]</i>

30:05.041 --> 30:06.333
<i>[kisses]</i>

30:08.791 --> 30:09.666
<i>[Olga] Look.</i>

30:10.000 --> 30:11.791
<i>They all say the same thing.</i>

30:12.083 --> 30:16.166
<i>I answered him once</i>
<i>and he should consider himself lucky.</i>

30:16.833 --> 30:18.125
<i>[Roberto] What did you write?</i>

30:18.791 --> 30:20.458
<i>I still love him,</i>

30:20.541 --> 30:23.000
<i>but no way are Irma and I going</i>

30:23.083 --> 30:24.625
<i>to the United States.</i>

30:25.875 --> 30:29.041
<i>My daughter won't be raised by a traitor.</i>

30:29.916 --> 30:33.125
<i>Or live close to a terrorist,</i>
<i>like José Basulto.</i>

30:33.500 --> 30:36.583
<i>[Roberto] I heard René left Basulto</i>
<i>and joined the PUND.</i>

30:37.291 --> 30:38.750
<i>Better pay, supposedly.</i>

30:39.541 --> 30:43.958
<i>With them, you never know</i>
<i>where the fight for a free Cuba ends</i>

30:44.041 --> 30:45.875
<i>and drug smuggling begins.</i>

30:47.041 --> 30:50.000
<i>Know where René will end up?</i>
<i>In jail!</i>

30:50.333 --> 30:53.083
<i>And I won't care a bit.</i>

30:53.541 --> 30:54.375
<i>[engine roaring]</i>

30:58.416 --> 30:59.500
<i>[in English] </i>Keep going south.

30:59.583 --> 31:00.416
<i>South?</i>

31:01.958 --> 31:03.250
<i>It's not our flight plan.</i>

31:03.625 --> 31:06.125
<i>Did you follow the flight plan</i>
<i>when you were working for the Hermanos?</i>

31:06.666 --> 31:07.500
<i>Not really.</i>

31:08.583 --> 31:10.250
<i>So keep heading south.</i>

31:14.708 --> 31:17.250
<i>[alert beeping]</i>

31:22.875 --> 31:24.625
<i>[men shouting]</i>

31:26.625 --> 31:27.833
<i>[co-pilot speaking Spanish] Hurry up!</i>

31:28.958 --> 31:31.666
<i>Faster!</i>

31:35.625 --> 31:37.125
<i>[co-pilot in English] Let's go!</i>

31:37.208 --> 31:38.208
<i>[indistinct shouting]</i>

31:50.500 --> 31:51.333
<i>[tires squeal]</i>

31:53.500 --> 31:54.333
<i>[tires squeal]</i>

31:55.500 --> 31:57.791
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

31:57.875 --> 32:01.041
<i>[men shouting]</i>

32:03.958 --> 32:05.541
<i>[car engine revs]</i>

32:06.125 --> 32:06.958
<i>[peels out]</i>

32:14.166 --> 32:15.250
<i>[in Spanish] You saw nothing.</i>

32:15.333 --> 32:16.708
<i>[in English] I saw nothing.</i>

32:17.666 --> 32:19.416
<i>Are you inspired today?</i>

32:19.500 --> 32:20.750
<i>-[Ana laughs]</i>
<i>-Let me see.</i>

32:20.833 --> 32:22.416
<i>[laughing] Don't start.</i>

32:22.500 --> 32:24.500
<i>-I'm super inspired.</i>
<i>-[Ana laughs]</i>

32:24.583 --> 32:25.416
<i>[doorbell rings]</i>

32:32.166 --> 32:33.125
<i>[Roque] </i>Coño.

32:33.958 --> 32:34.958
<i>René...</i>

32:35.416 --> 32:37.166
<i>-[René in Spanish] Hello, darling.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

32:37.250 --> 32:38.791
<i>-[René] How are you?</i>
<i>-Good.</i>

32:38.875 --> 32:41.708
<i>-Hope you're hungry.</i>
<i>-Pretty hungry.</i>

32:41.791 --> 32:44.041
<i>-[in English] Will you get us some drinks?</i>
<i>-Yeah, right away.</i>

32:44.125 --> 32:45.416
<i>-Gracias.</i>
<i>-[Ana blows a kiss]</i>

32:47.791 --> 32:49.208
<i>[in Spanish] Speak Russian?</i>

32:49.791 --> 32:52.041
<i>[in Russian] I learned it in Cuba.</i>
<i>Like you.</i>

32:52.125 --> 32:53.083
<i>Good.</i>

32:54.916 --> 32:56.375
<i>It's about the PUND.</i>

32:56.875 --> 33:00.291
<i>You know the rumor.</i>
<i>They're just a front.</i>

33:00.375 --> 33:02.291
<i>Working with the Colombians.</i>

33:02.375 --> 33:04.583
<i>Smuggling cocaine.</i>

33:04.666 --> 33:07.958
<i>You said you didn't believe it.</i>

33:08.041 --> 33:09.208
<i>First, I didn't.</i>

33:09.291 --> 33:10.416
<i>Tequila.</i>

33:13.416 --> 33:15.000
<i>Mariquitas de platanos!</i>

33:15.083 --> 33:17.333
<i>-[Ana in Spanish] Like them?</i>
<i>-Love them.</i>

33:17.958 --> 33:19.333
<i>She's some cook!</i>

33:19.416 --> 33:20.250
<i>[René] I bet.</i>

33:20.333 --> 33:21.458
<i>[laughing] Cheers!</i>

33:21.541 --> 33:22.500
<i>Hermano.</i>

33:22.583 --> 33:23.416
<i>[Ana] Salud.</i>

33:26.458 --> 33:30.041
<i>[in English] Ana, can you leave us alone</i>
<i>for a sec? We need to talk.</i>

33:30.125 --> 33:32.000
<i>Yes. I'm sorry.</i>

33:34.041 --> 33:36.916
<i>[in Russian] I flew</i>
<i>one of their loads myself.</i>

33:37.041 --> 33:41.458
<i>[inhales] I don't want to get arrested</i>
<i>for drug smuggling.</i>

33:41.541 --> 33:42.458
<i>Roque--</i>

33:42.541 --> 33:46.833
<i>I didn't come to the States</i>
<i>to end up in jail.</i>

33:47.333 --> 33:49.208
<i>I told you.</i>

33:49.833 --> 33:52.833
<i>My cousin Denayf works for the FBI.</i>

33:53.750 --> 33:56.208
<i>He can put you in touch with his boss.</i>

33:57.375 --> 34:00.916
<i>[upbeat Latin music playing]</i>

34:01.541 --> 34:02.625
<i>[in Spanish] How are you?</i>

34:03.583 --> 34:04.875
<i>René Gonzales.</i>

34:05.375 --> 34:06.666
<i>Nice to meet you.</i>

34:08.708 --> 34:09.916
<i>[René clears his throat]</i>

34:11.125 --> 34:14.250
<i>What I need is an airtight case.</i>

34:15.000 --> 34:15.833
<i>[inhales slowly]</i>

34:16.541 --> 34:17.541
<i>So René...</i>

34:19.166 --> 34:20.791
<i>How far will you go for us?</i>

34:21.250 --> 34:23.541
<i>I won't take part</i>
<i>in their criminal activities.</i>

34:24.000 --> 34:25.833
<i>[FBI agent] I'll cut to the chase.</i>

34:25.916 --> 34:29.041
<i>I'm offering you to be an FBI informer.</i>

34:30.541 --> 34:33.500
<i>[FBI agent] You'll get $1,500 a week.</i>

34:34.000 --> 34:35.541
<i>All I ask of you</i>

34:36.541 --> 34:40.166
<i>is to brief me on the PUND's activities.</i>

34:40.250 --> 34:41.458
<i>Informer.</i>

34:46.250 --> 34:47.625
<i>Not my thing.</i>

34:47.875 --> 34:49.791
<i>Your friend Juan Pablo Roque</i>

34:49.875 --> 34:53.750
<i>has been working for us for a year.</i>

34:54.916 --> 34:56.666
<i>-For the same money.</i>
<i>-[René laughs]</i>

34:57.083 --> 34:58.250
<i>Now I get it.</i>

34:58.333 --> 34:59.458
<i>[FBI agent] Get what?</i>

34:59.541 --> 35:00.750
<i>His lifestyle.</i>

35:03.583 --> 35:05.375
<i>[Viamonte in English] </i>I'll need you
tomorrow.

35:05.458 --> 35:07.125
<i>[René] </i>For a special operation?

35:07.708 --> 35:09.166
<i>[Viamonte] </i>All operations are special.

35:10.083 --> 35:11.666
<i>Landing in Honduras again?</i>

35:12.666 --> 35:13.833
<i>And then in Nassau.</i>

35:14.250 --> 35:16.250
<i>The money's good,</i>
<i>but it's too risky for me.</i>

35:17.958 --> 35:19.583
<i>Got any other offers?</i>

35:20.333 --> 35:24.583
<i>Ramón Saul Sánchez reached out to me.</i>
Movimiento<i> </i>Democracia<i> needs good pilots.</i>

35:24.666 --> 35:25.833
<i>Ramoncito?</i>

35:25.916 --> 35:27.708
<i>[in Spanish] Don't be a cocksucker.</i>

35:29.125 --> 35:31.250
<i>[in English] I told you, man.</i>
<i>I'm working for the liberation of Cuba.</i>

35:31.625 --> 35:33.250
<i>And I'm trying to finance it.</i>

35:33.333 --> 35:34.208
<i>With drug money.</i>

35:35.166 --> 35:36.375
<i>I take the money where I can find it.</i>

35:37.666 --> 35:38.875
<i>[René] </i>From Colombians.

35:38.958 --> 35:41.416
<i>[Viamonte] </i>How else do you think
I can pay you 175 a week?

35:42.958 --> 35:44.583
<i>[Viamonte] Can I count on you tomorrow?</i>

35:47.000 --> 35:47.833
<i>No.</i>

35:53.125 --> 35:54.416
<i>[tires squeal]</i>

35:56.250 --> 35:57.958
<i>-[agent 1] Get out!</i>
<i>-[agent 2] Check in the back.</i>

35:58.041 --> 35:59.625
<i>[sirens]</i>

35:59.708 --> 36:00.708
<i>[agent] Turn around.</i>

36:06.625 --> 36:08.625
<i>[handcuffs click and fasten]</i>

36:19.958 --> 36:22.583
<i>[in Spanish] Tell me you're sure.</i>
<i>You made up your mind.</i>

36:22.666 --> 36:24.000
<i>I'm no rat.</i>

36:25.166 --> 36:29.750
<i>Who says working for the FBI</i>
<i>is being a rat?</i>

36:29.833 --> 36:32.000
<i>At least it pays well.</i>

36:32.333 --> 36:36.333
<i>I didn't sacrifice my life in Cuba</i>
<i>to make money here.</i>

36:37.208 --> 36:38.625
<i>Life there is a disaster.</i>

36:38.708 --> 36:40.000
<i>No gas.</i>

36:40.625 --> 36:43.416
<i>Eight hours of electricity a day.</i>

36:43.500 --> 36:44.708
<i>No medicine.</i>

36:44.791 --> 36:47.166
<i>No food. People are starving.</i>

36:47.250 --> 36:48.833
<i>Let me ask you a question.</i>

36:49.416 --> 36:52.125
<i>Know how much</i>
Movimiento Democracia <i>charges</i>

36:52.208 --> 36:54.250
<i>to bring people from Cuba to Florida?</i>

36:54.333 --> 36:55.625
<i>A lot.</i>

36:56.666 --> 36:58.416
<i>But it's for a good cause.</i>

37:03.916 --> 37:04.875
<i>My job...</i>

37:05.833 --> 37:06.916
<i>is to save lives.</i>

37:08.916 --> 37:10.541
<i>[Roque in English]</i>
<i>Who's going to be there?</i>

37:11.541 --> 37:12.375
<i>[Roque] Okay.</i>

37:15.166 --> 37:16.041
<i>No, I can go.</i>

37:17.583 --> 37:19.250
<i>Is it good for you tomorrow?</i>

37:21.208 --> 37:22.041
<i>How you doing?</i>

37:22.125 --> 37:25.916
<i>I'm almost finished</i>
<i>with the guest list for the reception.</i>

37:27.875 --> 37:32.125
<i>[sighs] Otherwise, I've got good news.</i>
<i>You wanna know what it is?</i>

37:35.250 --> 37:36.083
<i>Of course I do.</i>

37:36.166 --> 37:39.166
<i>Luis Alexander is going to let us use</i>
<i>the Alexander Mansion.</i>

37:41.416 --> 37:43.500
<i>The Alexander Mansion in South Miami!</i>

37:43.583 --> 37:46.833
<i>I know! That's really good news.</i>
<i>-[Ana] Yes!</i>

37:46.916 --> 37:48.541
<i>And Jorge Mas Canosa will be there.</i>

37:48.625 --> 37:50.000
<i>Never met him.</i>

37:51.791 --> 37:54.625
<i>They're saying</i>
<i>it's gonna be the wedding of the decade.</i>

38:04.958 --> 38:06.458
<i>[Ana] Can I ask you a question?</i>

38:07.208 --> 38:08.125
<i>Of course you can.</i>

38:08.750 --> 38:10.375
<i>Why do you have a cellphone?</i>

38:10.708 --> 38:12.416
<i>I don't know anyone else with one.</i>

38:12.500 --> 38:14.375
<i>My friends' husbands </i>
<i>are happy with pagers.</i>

38:14.458 --> 38:16.458
<i>-It's useful.</i>
<i>-Hmm?</i>

38:17.166 --> 38:19.708
<i>You can reach me whenever you want</i>
<i>and I can call you--</i>

38:19.791 --> 38:23.958
<i>I know how cellphones work. I got that.</i>
<i>It's very expensive.</i>

38:24.041 --> 38:26.375
<i>-Not to mention the contract.</i>
<i>-It's useful.</i>

38:28.708 --> 38:31.791
<i>You know,</i>
<i>I am aware of how much things cost.</i>

38:32.333 --> 38:37.291
<i>-[Ana] You have a new Rolex.</i>
<i>-Yeah, I do. It's a Rolex Submariner--</i>

38:37.375 --> 38:39.708
<i>Silver with a blue dial.</i>

38:40.916 --> 38:42.875
<i>You're very observant.</i>

38:43.041 --> 38:45.791
<i>That costs $8000, at least.</i>

38:45.875 --> 38:48.291
<i>-You're not far off.</i>
<i>-You bought it without telling me.</i>

38:48.875 --> 38:50.875
<i>I don't tell you everything.</i>

39:05.708 --> 39:07.458
<i>Where's the money coming from?</i>

39:10.083 --> 39:13.750
<i>I know that there are fewer </i>balseros
<i>since the treaty with Cuba--</i>

39:13.833 --> 39:15.250
<i>A lot fewer, yes.</i>

39:15.333 --> 39:16.416
<i>Fewer sorties.</i>

39:16.500 --> 39:18.500
<i>The Hermanos went</i>
<i>from 2000 a year to 200--</i>

39:18.583 --> 39:20.916
<i>and your donations to organizations</i>
<i>that are helping them.</i>

39:21.000 --> 39:24.750
<i>-You are 100% right!</i>
<i>-I know! That's why I'm asking...</i>

39:25.250 --> 39:26.750
<i>Where do you get your money?</i>

39:28.666 --> 39:30.500
<i>And I want a straight answer.</i>

39:32.208 --> 39:33.916
<i>I already told you.</i>

39:34.000 --> 39:36.375
<i>I signed a contract for an autobiography.</i>

39:36.916 --> 39:40.583
<i>Excuse me. The one you’ve been writing</i>
<i>for six months? One hour a day max?</i>

39:40.666 --> 39:42.250
<i>-Yes, that's the one.</i>
<i>-Really?</i>

39:42.333 --> 39:45.000
<i>That is bullshit! Who are you kidding?</i>

39:45.083 --> 39:47.500
<i>I've never heard of anyone making money</i>
<i>from writing.</i>

39:47.583 --> 39:49.458
<i>Except you're a movie star</i>
<i>and you make a biography--</i>

39:49.541 --> 39:52.000
<i>Well, I am. I'm a star, my love.</i>

39:52.416 --> 39:53.375
<i>You're marrying a star.</i>

39:54.416 --> 39:56.500
<i>And the book that I'm writing</i>
<i>for six months</i>

39:56.583 --> 39:58.583
<i>-one hour per day is gonna be dynamite...</i>
<i>-[Ana] You're lying.</i>

39:58.666 --> 40:01.250
<i>'cause I’m gonna tell everything</i>
<i>about the low morale in Cuban aviation--</i>

40:01.333 --> 40:04.541
<i>The only way you have of making</i>
<i>that kind of money is with drugs.</i>

40:06.166 --> 40:07.708
<i>So I wanna know.</i>

40:08.500 --> 40:10.250
<i>What is it? Cocaine?</i>

40:12.750 --> 40:14.125
<i>[glass clinks on the table]</i>

40:15.625 --> 40:17.375
<i>Do you want me to leave you?</i>

40:19.375 --> 40:20.375
<i>Right now?</i>

40:22.291 --> 40:23.125
<i>Answer!</i>

40:25.041 --> 40:27.333
<i>Do you know how much this gold chain is?</i>

40:29.250 --> 40:33.666
<i>I didn't flee Cuba to be a loser</i>
<i>in Miami, Ana.</i>

40:34.666 --> 40:38.333
<i>I'm wearing a $2000 suit.</i>
<i>Does it bother you?</i>

40:41.083 --> 40:42.958
<i>[sternly] Does it bother you?</i>

40:44.375 --> 40:46.208
<i>I'm not involved in drugs.</i>

40:50.041 --> 40:52.625
<i>[whispering] But you don't know everything</i>
<i>about me.</i>

40:56.333 --> 40:58.625
<i>And it's better for you that way.</i>

41:04.041 --> 41:06.166
<i>[René in Spanish] </i>This is Charlie 4-0-4-7.

41:06.541 --> 41:09.666
<i>This is Charlie 4-0-4-7.</i>
<i>Blue Shark, do you copy?</i>

41:09.750 --> 41:11.875
<i>This is Blue Shark, copy.</i>

41:11.958 --> 41:14.250
<i>[René] </i>Flying along 24th Parallel, 82W.

41:14.708 --> 41:15.958
<i>The sea is clear.</i>

41:17.083 --> 41:18.708
<i>I repeat: Sea is clear.</i>

41:21.916 --> 41:24.416
<i>No Coast Guard. Let's go!</i>

41:26.875 --> 41:27.750
<i>Chino!</i>

41:27.833 --> 41:29.833
<i>[engine revs]</i>

41:37.666 --> 41:44.666
<i>-[gunshots]</i>
<i>-[beachgoers screaming]</i>

41:45.416 --> 41:50.250
<i>-[alarm ringing]</i>
<i>-[shooting draws nearer]</i>

41:50.333 --> 41:57.333
<i>-[people screaming]</i>
<i>-[gunfire]</i>

41:59.000 --> 42:01.500
<i>[sinister music plays and fades out]</i>

42:06.958 --> 42:07.791
<i>[René sighs]</i>

42:08.291 --> 42:09.708
<i>Back from a mission?</i>

42:10.291 --> 42:12.166
<i>Don't you have your own sources?</i>

42:12.250 --> 42:14.500
<i>They say the operation was a success.</i>

42:15.666 --> 42:17.291
<i>No casualties. But damage.</i>

42:17.375 --> 42:19.333
<i>-Bad?</i>
<i>-Bad enough.</i>

42:20.125 --> 42:23.166
<i>The Cubans won't shout it from rooftops,</i>

42:23.250 --> 42:24.625
<i>as you can imagine.</i>

42:25.500 --> 42:28.250
<i>The </i>Movimiento<i> may be proud. Not me.</i>

42:30.291 --> 42:32.833
<i>Why, if it's not indiscreet?</i>

42:32.916 --> 42:36.416
<i>I didn't join the resistance</i>
<i>to abet terrorists.</i>

42:36.958 --> 42:38.625
<i>Just to save rafters.</i>

42:40.208 --> 42:41.125
<i>A beer?</i>

42:41.208 --> 42:43.500
<i>[Basulto murmurs indistinctly]</i>

42:46.500 --> 42:47.875
<i>[Basulto groans]</i>

42:49.083 --> 42:50.625
<i>Why did you want to see me?</i>

42:51.000 --> 42:52.541
<i>I got news from Olga.</i>

42:53.208 --> 42:54.125
<i>Damn!</i>

42:54.625 --> 42:56.750
<i>She's finally writing back?</i>

42:57.375 --> 42:58.208
<i>Yes.</i>

43:00.000 --> 43:01.625
<i>Her whole life is in Cuba.</i>

43:02.208 --> 43:03.416
<i>Her career,</i>

43:03.916 --> 43:05.666
<i>her friends, family.</i>

43:06.666 --> 43:09.875
<i>-It must be tough for her.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

43:10.916 --> 43:12.500
<i>[clears throat] But...</i>

43:13.000 --> 43:14.583
<i>she's made a decision.</i>

43:14.958 --> 43:15.791
<i>Really?</i>

43:17.166 --> 43:18.833
<i>She'll come and live with me.</i>

43:20.791 --> 43:22.000
<i>Okay, but...</i>

43:22.583 --> 43:25.333
<i>that's much easier said than done.</i>

43:25.416 --> 43:26.916
<i>I'm a U.S. citizen.</i>

43:27.000 --> 43:27.833
<i>And?</i>

43:28.291 --> 43:30.791
<i>The new law prioritizes U.S. citizens.</i>

43:30.875 --> 43:32.375
<i>It's not so simple.</i>

43:33.041 --> 43:34.333
<i>There are quotas,</i>

43:34.708 --> 43:37.291
<i>waiting lists, bureaucracy.</i>

43:37.375 --> 43:39.166
<i>Which is why I need your help.</i>

43:43.750 --> 43:45.583
<i>You have connections in Washington.</i>

43:45.666 --> 43:47.875
<i>Does she have a Cuban exit visa?</i>

43:48.500 --> 43:49.375
<i>No.</i>

43:49.625 --> 43:54.250
<i>No use pulling strings</i>
<i>if they won't let her leave.</i>

43:55.333 --> 43:56.375
<i>[applause]</i>

43:56.458 --> 44:00.958
<i>[horns honking]</i>

44:01.041 --> 44:03.041
<i>[people cheering]</i>

44:13.000 --> 44:14.333
<i>[cameras clicking]</i>

44:14.416 --> 44:17.208
<i>[cheering and applause grow louder]</i>

44:24.166 --> 44:25.958
<i>[reporter speaking in Spanish]</i>

44:26.041 --> 44:27.000
<i>[whistling]</i>

44:30.833 --> 44:34.416
<i>[priest in Spanish]</i>
<i>Bless and sanctify, Lord,</i>

44:34.500 --> 44:39.000
<i>the love uniting</i>
<i>Juan Pablo and Ana Margarita.</i>

44:40.208 --> 44:41.041
<i>[Ana clears her throat]</i>

44:41.833 --> 44:44.666
<i>-[Ana laughs]</i>
<i>-[whistles from the audience]</i>

44:46.041 --> 44:48.083
<i>[sighs] Juan Pablo,</i>

44:48.541 --> 44:50.416
<i>this ring is a symbol</i>

44:50.500 --> 44:53.250
<i>of my love and my loyalty.</i>

44:54.333 --> 44:57.250
<i>In the name of the Father,</i>
<i>the Son and the Holy Ghost.</i>

44:58.000 --> 45:00.333
<i>-May I?</i>
<i>-[priest] You may kiss the bride.</i>

45:00.416 --> 45:05.083
<i>[organ playing the wedding march]</i>

45:05.166 --> 45:09.291
<i>[cheering and applause]</i>

45:14.541 --> 45:16.208
<i>[women cheering louder]</i>

45:16.291 --> 45:18.291
<i>[church bells tolling]</i>

45:18.375 --> 45:20.375
<i>[cameras clicking]</i>

45:25.208 --> 45:28.791
<i>[horns honking]</i>

45:47.958 --> 45:50.541
<i>[Latin music playing]</i>

45:50.625 --> 45:53.041
<i>[children playing]</i>

45:53.125 --> 45:56.125
<i>[chatter]</i>

46:00.708 --> 46:03.708
<i>-[glasses clinking]</i>
<i>-[cheering]</i>

46:04.708 --> 46:08.000
<i>[in Spanish] Come,</i>
<i>I'd like to introduce you to someone.</i>

46:09.958 --> 46:12.291
<i>[party noise faint in background]</i>

46:20.916 --> 46:24.333
<i>Juan Pablo,</i>
<i>It is my honor to introduce you</i>

46:24.416 --> 46:27.958
<i>to the President of the CANF,</i>
<i>Jorge Mas Canosa.</i>

46:28.041 --> 46:32.541
<i>This man will lead us</i>
<i>to a free and democratic Cuba.</i>

46:32.625 --> 46:34.708
<i>An honor to have you here.</i>

46:35.916 --> 46:38.791
<i>A promise of success for our marriage.</i>

46:38.875 --> 46:42.000
<i>My friend, Basulto, says</i>
<i>you're our best pilot.</i>

46:42.500 --> 46:44.000
<i>Available at any hour.</i>

46:44.083 --> 46:46.166
<i>Sir, with all due respect,</i>

46:47.125 --> 46:48.208
<i>from now on,</i>

46:48.583 --> 46:50.708
<i>you'll have to check with my wife</i>
<i>about that.</i>

46:50.791 --> 46:52.500
<i>[all laughing]</i>

46:52.833 --> 46:53.666
<i>[door creaking]</i>

47:03.333 --> 47:04.458
<i>Congratulations.</i>

47:04.541 --> 47:07.208
<i>-Thank you.</i>
<i>-Thank you for coming.</i>

47:12.333 --> 47:14.333
<i>[Roque clears his throat]</i>

47:16.041 --> 47:20.833
<i>[trumpet playing Latin music]</i>

47:23.166 --> 47:25.708
<i>-He's very handsome.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

47:25.791 --> 47:30.041
<i>[conversation fades into the background]</i>

47:30.125 --> 47:36.208
<i>[soulful Spanish vocals join music]</i>

47:36.291 --> 47:37.625
<i>Here's the groom.</i>

47:44.500 --> 47:48.500
<i>[cheering and whooping]</i>

48:06.500 --> 48:08.166
<i>[in Russian] I'm very happy for you.</i>

48:09.791 --> 48:11.833
<i>If only my wife were here.</i>

48:13.541 --> 48:15.208
<i>She'll come, trust me.</i>

48:16.666 --> 48:18.666
<i>[background laughter]</i>

48:19.458 --> 48:21.208
<i>Great crowd.</i>

48:23.416 --> 48:25.916
<i>Jorge Mas Canosa, no less!</i>

48:27.583 --> 48:30.083
<i>He rarely goes out in public.</i>

48:30.500 --> 48:33.208
<i>It's an honor.</i>

48:34.208 --> 48:36.375
<i>He wanted a picture with us.</i>

48:36.458 --> 48:39.333
<i>[laughs] He even called the press.</i>

48:39.416 --> 48:44.208
<i>[salsa music playing]</i>

48:46.625 --> 48:48.208
<i>[laughing]</i>

48:55.916 --> 48:56.958
<i>[women laughing]</i>

49:02.291 --> 49:03.708
<i>[indistinct in Spanish]</i>

49:26.125 --> 49:27.541
<i>[indistinct in Spanish]</i>

49:46.500 --> 49:47.541
<i>[in English] Come on!</i>

49:48.791 --> 49:49.625
<i>[groans]</i>

50:12.000 --> 50:14.000
<i>[Ana sighs]</i>

50:16.166 --> 50:17.833
<i>[waves crashing in distance]</i>

50:17.916 --> 50:19.916
<i>-[Roque] Ana.</i>
<i>-[Ana] Oh, my God.</i>

50:22.708 --> 50:26.250
<i>-[wheel grinding]</i>
<i>-[loud splashing]</i>

50:39.333 --> 50:40.916
<i>[in Spanish] Got the missing document?</i>

50:41.375 --> 50:42.791
<i>It arrived this morning.</i>

50:42.875 --> 50:45.875
<i>This morning! I asked for it 3 weeks ago.</i>

50:45.958 --> 50:49.500
<i>Now you can officially quit the tannery.</i>

50:49.916 --> 50:52.416
<i>Are you making the right decision?</i>

50:52.875 --> 50:54.250
<i>Yes, I am.</i>

50:54.333 --> 50:57.583
<i>We need you.</i>
<i>And I know you like your job.</i>

50:58.458 --> 51:01.791
<i>What will you do in Miami?</i>
<i>Start over from scratch?</i>

51:01.875 --> 51:05.208
<i>My daughter needs a father. I told you.</i>

51:05.291 --> 51:07.875
<i>[man] Yes, but that father? A traitor.</i>

51:07.958 --> 51:09.083
<i>Only one she has.</i>

51:09.166 --> 51:10.291
<i>So,</i>

51:10.750 --> 51:12.625
<i>you're sacrificing yourself.</i>

51:13.208 --> 51:16.541
<i>That's one way of looking at it.</i>
<i>Thank you, Luis.</i>

51:16.625 --> 51:19.625
<i>[children talking]</i>

51:30.958 --> 51:33.375
<i>-Yanicé Rodríguez.</i>
<i>-Here.</i>

51:36.083 --> 51:37.791
<i>Caridad de la Nuez.</i>

51:39.666 --> 51:40.750
<i>Not here?</i>

51:41.333 --> 51:43.166
<i>Olga Salanueva.</i>

51:45.416 --> 51:47.000
<i>You go to that desk.</i>

51:48.125 --> 51:49.333
<i>You come here.</i>

51:50.500 --> 51:52.083
<i>-You go there.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

51:52.958 --> 51:57.083
<i>Comrade, I brought the document</i>
<i>you requested last time.</i>

51:58.250 --> 51:59.833
<i>And my daughter, as you asked.</i>

52:00.291 --> 52:03.083
<i>Thank you. This will help your case.</i>

52:04.625 --> 52:06.166
<i>But it's not the right one.</i>

52:06.708 --> 52:07.541
<i>What?</i>

52:07.708 --> 52:10.458
<i>I need one</i>
<i>from the Ministry of Light Industry.</i>

52:10.541 --> 52:12.458
<i>-You have it now.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

52:12.541 --> 52:14.875
<i>This is from the Tannery Directorate.</i>

52:15.833 --> 52:18.958
<i>But the Directorate</i>
<i>is part of the Ministry.</i>

52:19.041 --> 52:20.583
<i>Perhaps, but it's different.</i>

52:20.666 --> 52:23.083
<i>-I need--</i>
<i>-No one will ever believe me.</i>

52:23.166 --> 52:24.416
<i>Can I finish?</i>

52:24.708 --> 52:26.416
<i>[sighs] I'm sorry.</i>

52:27.166 --> 52:30.791
<i>I need a waiver from the Ministry</i>
<i>releasing you from your contract</i>

52:30.875 --> 52:33.375
<i>and stating you have no debts</i>
<i>with the State.</i>

52:33.458 --> 52:34.875
<i>I have no debts at all.</i>

52:35.375 --> 52:37.875
<i>So the document will be easy to get.</i>

52:37.958 --> 52:42.750
<i>[phone rings]</i>

52:45.166 --> 52:46.000
<i>Yes?</i>

52:46.083 --> 52:50.041
<i>I couldn't wait to tell you the good news.</i>

52:50.125 --> 52:51.500
<i>I found a job.</i>

52:52.000 --> 52:54.583
<i>For a cargo airline, Arrow Air.</i>

52:55.125 --> 52:57.958
<i>We can get by until you get a job.</i>

52:58.041 --> 53:01.416
<i>And if I pass my engineer exam,</i>
<i>you won't even have to work.</i>

53:02.500 --> 53:04.208
<i>[René] </i>You're not happy?

53:04.791 --> 53:08.375
<i>[sighing] Listen, René...</i>
<i>I went to the Ministry yesterday.</i>

53:08.583 --> 53:10.583
<i>It didn't go well.</i>

53:11.083 --> 53:12.416
<i>[door creaking]</i>

53:12.500 --> 53:13.958
<i>It's your father.</i>

53:14.750 --> 53:17.791
<i>Leave me alone.</i>

53:19.875 --> 53:20.916
<i>Another delay?</i>

53:21.000 --> 53:22.416
<i>[Olga] </i>Even worse!

53:22.916 --> 53:25.791
<i>I had all the documents</i>

53:25.875 --> 53:28.416
<i>but they invented a new one.</i>

53:29.333 --> 53:30.416
<i>I'm so discouraged.</i>

53:30.500 --> 53:32.875
<i>Please. Not now.</i>

53:32.958 --> 53:35.166
<i>We're getting so close.</i>

53:35.333 --> 53:37.000
<i>You know the real problem.</i>

53:37.083 --> 53:39.250
<i>The problem is you.</i>

53:39.333 --> 53:43.083
<i>Not the documents. It's you.</i>
<i>[sighs]</i>

53:43.500 --> 53:46.458
<i>They'll never let me leave this country.</i>

54:07.333 --> 54:08.166
<i>[door creaks open]</i>

54:09.958 --> 54:13.958
<i>[ominous music playing softly]</i>

55:29.708 --> 55:30.625
<i>[man in Spanish] </i>What's your name?

55:31.000 --> 55:32.541
<i>Manuel Viramontez.</i>

55:32.625 --> 55:33.750
<i>Your parents?</i>

55:33.833 --> 55:35.833
<i>Pedro Viramontez and Rosalina Carrea.</i>

55:36.125 --> 55:37.500
<i>Place and date of birth?</i>

55:37.958 --> 55:41.916
<i>Cameron County, Texas.</i>
<i>January 26, 1967.</i>

55:42.250 --> 55:45.791
<i>My parents returned to Puerto Rico in '70.</i>
<i>Where they're from.</i>

55:45.875 --> 55:48.166
<i>I'm an American citizen.</i>

55:48.916 --> 55:50.708
<i>[officer] Your social security number?</i>

55:50.833 --> 55:53.708
<i>[in English] 584-56-5846.</i>

55:55.041 --> 55:56.750
<i>[officer in Spanish] Your address </i>
<i>in Puerto Rico?</i>

55:57.166 --> 55:59.958
<i>Darlington Building on Boriqueña Avenue,</i>

56:00.041 --> 56:03.708
<i>00925, Apartment 6C,</i>
<i>Rio Piedras.</i>

56:04.333 --> 56:05.875
<i>[officer] Phone number?</i>

56:06.083 --> 56:08.166
<i>658-1117.</i>

56:08.833 --> 56:10.000
<i>[officer] The building?</i>

56:10.333 --> 56:13.291
<i>A white building, eleven floors.</i>
<i>[inhales]</i>

56:13.375 --> 56:15.541
<i>On the first floor</i>
<i>there's a salsa station,</i>

56:15.625 --> 56:16.833
<i>Radio Voz...</i>

56:16.916 --> 56:21.500
<i>Very good, Lieutenant Hernandez.</i>
<i>How long have you been with us?</i>

56:21.583 --> 56:24.541
<i>Six months... studying my role.</i>

56:24.625 --> 56:25.583
<i>Like an actor.</i>

56:25.666 --> 56:28.416
<i>-Better than many actors.</i>
<i>-[all laugh]</i>

56:30.166 --> 56:31.791
<i>I see here</i>

56:32.291 --> 56:35.416
<i>that you joined a video rental club.</i>

56:35.500 --> 56:38.833
<i>Two glass doors.</i>
<i>You had to knock to get in.</i>

56:38.916 --> 56:40.708
<i>$3 a film.</i>

56:41.416 --> 56:43.916
<i>Well, thank you. You're dismissed.</i>

56:44.000 --> 56:44.875
<i>Sir...</i>

56:47.958 --> 56:48.791
<i>So?</i>

56:49.250 --> 56:52.458
<i>His Puerto Rican accent is perfect.</i>

56:54.750 --> 56:57.916
<i>I think he's ready to move to Miami.</i>

56:58.291 --> 56:59.583
<i>To run the Wasp Network.</i>

56:59.833 --> 57:03.833
<i>[Latin music playing]</i>

57:06.250 --> 57:08.416
<i>-[waiter] If you please.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

57:09.250 --> 57:10.083
<i>Thank you.</i>

57:12.208 --> 57:13.083
<i>Let's toast.</i>

57:13.166 --> 57:14.416
<i>To what?</i>

57:15.000 --> 57:16.416
<i>[Hernández] First, we toast.</i>

57:20.250 --> 57:21.333
<i>Listen Adriana,</i>

57:22.583 --> 57:25.916
<i>my International Relations thesis</i>
<i>was approved.</i>

57:26.708 --> 57:28.666
<i>So no more money problems?</i>

57:29.083 --> 57:30.625
<i>No more money problems.</i>

57:31.625 --> 57:33.083
<i>University pays for travel.</i>

57:34.333 --> 57:35.458
<i>Your travel?</i>

57:35.541 --> 57:36.625
<i>I'm going away.</i>

57:37.625 --> 57:38.875
<i>For several months.</i>

57:39.416 --> 57:40.333
<i>But...</i>

57:45.625 --> 57:47.250
<i>we said we'd have a child.</i>

57:47.666 --> 57:48.833
<i>[Hernández] We will.</i>

57:50.666 --> 57:52.250
<i>When I come back.</i>

57:52.541 --> 57:53.833
<i>When you come back.</i>

57:55.166 --> 57:56.000
<i>Of course.</i>

57:57.500 --> 58:01.583
<i>[woman crying]</i>

58:06.666 --> 58:12.666
<i>[crying gets louder]</i>

58:14.791 --> 58:16.208
<i>[sniffling]</i>

58:19.166 --> 58:20.041
<i>[sighing]</i>

58:21.916 --> 58:23.625
<i>[Adriana] I don't want to hurt you.</i>

58:23.958 --> 58:25.958
<i>-[Adriana] I'd hoped--</i>
<i>-For what?</i>

58:26.833 --> 58:28.708
<i>You'd finish your studies here,</i>

58:29.500 --> 58:32.041
<i>become a diplomat,</i>
<i>as you always said.</i>

58:32.125 --> 58:33.583
<i>I will do that.</i>

58:33.666 --> 58:34.500
<i>No.</i>

58:34.708 --> 58:35.625
<i>You're going away.</i>

58:43.791 --> 58:44.916
<i>[sniffling]</i>

58:46.416 --> 58:47.333
<i>Adriana,</i>

58:49.291 --> 58:51.958
<i>what I'm telling you</i>
<i>mustn't leave this room.</i>

58:52.375 --> 58:56.083
<i>For our love's sake,</i>
<i>it must never leave this room.</i>

58:57.666 --> 58:59.000
<i>You have my word.</i>

58:59.541 --> 59:02.875
<i>Anti-Castroist groups in Miami</i>

59:02.958 --> 59:05.166
<i>want to choke Cuba's economy.</i>

59:05.916 --> 59:10.125
<i>It's why they're attacking</i>
<i>our tourism industry.</i>

59:11.125 --> 59:14.583
<i>They want the world to think</i>
<i>Cuba is dangerous.</i>

59:16.208 --> 59:20.041
<i>The only way to stop them is to infiltrate</i>

59:21.208 --> 59:23.833
<i>their organizations in Florida.</i>

59:25.041 --> 59:26.750
<i>And find out what they're planning.</i>

59:27.875 --> 59:29.833
<i>[Hernández] We already have</i>
<i>men on the ground.</i>

59:30.458 --> 59:32.666
<i>They're waiting to be coordinated.</i>

59:41.000 --> 59:41.833
<i>They asked me</i>

59:43.791 --> 59:45.625
<i>to run this network.</i>

59:47.041 --> 59:48.250
<i>And I said yes.</i>

59:50.833 --> 59:52.250
<i>The Wasp Network.</i>

59:54.541 --> 59:58.541
<i>["Wipe Out" playing]</i>

1:00:16.291 --> 1:00:20.083
<i>[narrator in English] </i>René González
arrives on December 8, 1990.

1:00:20.166 --> 1:00:23.583
<i>Manuel Viramontez in December of 1991,</i>

1:00:23.666 --> 1:00:27.375
<i>and Juan Pablo Roque in February of 1992.</i>

1:00:27.458 --> 1:00:30.958
<i>The other agents arrive throughout 1992.</i>

1:00:31.583 --> 1:00:34.500
<i>First Linda and Nilo Hernández. </i>

1:00:34.583 --> 1:00:38.875
<i>Their cover: running a medical instruments </i>
<i>export company to Cuba.</i>

1:00:38.958 --> 1:00:44.000
<i>Their mission: infiltrate Alpha 66,</i>
<i>the most aggressive terrorist group.</i>

1:00:44.083 --> 1:00:45.208
<i>One, two, three...</i>

1:00:45.291 --> 1:00:50.125
<i>Antonio Guerrero moves to Key West,</i>
<i>the base of anti-Castro radio stations.</i>

1:00:50.208 --> 1:00:53.125
<i>He starts out as a salsa teacher</i>

1:00:53.916 --> 1:00:58.666
<i>then gets hired as a lathe operator</i>
<i>at the Boca Chica military airport.</i>

1:01:00.500 --> 1:01:03.583
<i>Ramón Labanino Salazar,</i>
<i>black belt in karate, </i>

1:01:03.666 --> 1:01:07.041
<i>fakes his defection and</i>
<i>joins the network in Tampa</i>

1:01:07.833 --> 1:01:11.500
<i>where his mission is to keep an eye</i>
<i>on Luis Posada Carriles</i>

1:01:11.583 --> 1:01:15.458
<i>one of the most nefarious figures</i>
<i>of anti-Castro terrorism.</i>

1:01:18.250 --> 1:01:19.958
<i>After four months of preparation,</i>

1:01:20.041 --> 1:01:23.833
<i>state security agents Amarylis Silverio</i>
<i>and Joseph Santos</i>

1:01:23.916 --> 1:01:27.791
<i>ride the third wave of emigration</i>
<i>to enter the United States.</i>

1:01:29.333 --> 1:01:32.458
<i>Amarylis quickly finds a job</i>
<i>as a receptionist.</i>

1:01:32.541 --> 1:01:33.375
<i>Can I help you?</i>

1:01:33.458 --> 1:01:36.250
<i>Whereas Joseph has to make do</i>
<i>with odd jobs.</i>

1:01:36.333 --> 1:01:38.083
<i>Others keep coming.</i>

1:01:38.166 --> 1:01:42.541
<i>By the end of 1992, the Wasp Network</i>
<i>is fully operational.</i>

1:01:47.791 --> 1:01:50.458
<i>The agents have no contact whatsoever</i>
<i>with one other.</i>

1:01:51.000 --> 1:01:55.625
<i>Only Labanino, González and Villareal</i>
<i>are responsible for collecting information</i>

1:01:55.708 --> 1:01:58.041
<i>and passing it on to Manuel Viramontez. </i>

1:02:01.375 --> 1:02:04.583
<i>Each agent communicates via pager</i>
<i>with his superior.</i>

1:02:05.041 --> 1:02:06.375
<i>[pager beeps]</i>

1:02:06.458 --> 1:02:09.333
<i>Every two weeks,</i>
<i>the agent receives a message</i>

1:02:09.416 --> 1:02:12.708
<i>indicating a spot to deliver</i> 
<i>the information he has collected </i>

1:02:12.791 --> 1:02:14.583
<i>and saved to a diskette.</i>

1:02:16.125 --> 1:02:20.208
<i>Manuel Viramontez gathers the information,</i>
<i>then transmits it to Cuba </i>

1:02:20.291 --> 1:02:22.416
<i>via shortwave radio.</i>

1:02:22.500 --> 1:02:23.958
<i>The files that were too large,</i>

1:02:24.041 --> 1:02:27.416
<i>he coded them, and mailed them</i>
<i>to a P.O. box in Central America</i>

1:02:27.500 --> 1:02:32.125
<i>where a Cuban diplomat would pick them up</i>
<i>and forward them via diplomatic pouch.</i>

1:02:35.083 --> 1:02:39.708
<i>During this period, the Wasp Network</i>
<i>was able to thwart 20 terrorist attacks,</i>

1:02:39.791 --> 1:02:43.500
<i>and to seize a large quantity</i>
<i>of explosives, weapons and cash.</i>

1:02:43.583 --> 1:02:45.625
<i>-[in Spanish] What's this?</i>
<i>-[agent 2] C4!</i>

1:02:51.333 --> 1:02:56.666
<i>In March '95, Cuban Americans</i>
<i>Martínez Rueda and Ramírez Oro</i>

1:02:56.750 --> 1:03:00.500
<i>entered Cuba clandestinely by sea</i>
<i>to bury a load of explosives</i>

1:03:00.583 --> 1:03:04.291
<i>they would use in an</i>
<i>attack on Hotel Melia in Varadero. </i>

1:03:07.333 --> 1:03:10.916
<i>A few weeks later,</i>
<i>they flew back to execute their mission, </i>

1:03:11.000 --> 1:03:14.750
<i>and were arrested</i>
<i>at José Martí Airport in La Havana.</i>

1:03:16.333 --> 1:03:19.083
<i>Both confessed to taking orders from CANF.</i>

1:03:22.666 --> 1:03:25.875
<i>Thanks to informations collected</i>
<i>by the Wasp Network,</i>

1:03:25.958 --> 1:03:30.333
<i>30 terrorists were arrested,</i>
<i>both Cuban emigrants and mercenaries,</i>

1:03:30.416 --> 1:03:33.000
<i>targeting tourist destinations in Cuba.</i>

1:03:47.958 --> 1:03:49.583
<i>-[man in Spanish] Welcome.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

1:03:49.916 --> 1:03:51.166
<i>[man] Have a seat.</i>

1:03:54.125 --> 1:03:55.000
<i>[Olga] Thank you.</i>

1:04:05.333 --> 1:04:06.208
<i>So...</i>

1:04:06.708 --> 1:04:09.208
<i>you're joining your husband in Miami.</i>

1:04:09.791 --> 1:04:12.750
<i>Yes, but I'm doing it for my daughter.</i>

1:04:12.916 --> 1:04:14.958
<i>So she's near her father.</i>

1:04:15.458 --> 1:04:17.916
<i>It's important that you know the truth.</i>

1:04:20.250 --> 1:04:22.541
<i>Your husband, René González,</i>

1:04:23.708 --> 1:04:24.833
<i>is not a traitor.</i>

1:04:27.458 --> 1:04:29.458
<i>Your husband is a hero.</i>

1:04:29.958 --> 1:04:31.000
<i>A hero?</i>

1:04:32.666 --> 1:04:35.375
<i>He sacrificed everything</i>
<i>for our Revolution.</i>

1:04:35.458 --> 1:04:38.708
<i>His relationship with you,</i>
<i>with your daughter.</i>

1:04:41.000 --> 1:04:43.083
<i>He is in Miami on a mission.</i>

1:04:44.583 --> 1:04:47.583
<i>To infiltrate terrorist organizations</i>

1:04:47.666 --> 1:04:50.375
<i>and warn us about their plans.</i>

1:04:52.916 --> 1:04:54.583
<i>He's helped save many lives.</i>

1:04:56.666 --> 1:04:59.208
<i>Now that you're joining him,</i>
<i>you must know.</i>

1:05:00.541 --> 1:05:02.541
<i>But most important...</i>

1:05:02.625 --> 1:05:06.625
<i>[draws breath] your daughter</i>
<i>must never find out.</i>

1:05:07.041 --> 1:05:07.875
<i>Never.</i>

1:05:09.291 --> 1:05:10.375
<i>Understand?</i>

1:05:13.958 --> 1:05:15.166
<i>Do I have your word?</i>

1:05:16.458 --> 1:05:17.416
<i>Yes.</i>

1:05:23.958 --> 1:05:27.250
<i>Truth is, I made the same choice </i>
<i>as your husband.</i>

1:05:27.333 --> 1:05:29.416
<i>-[Olga] Mmm.</i>
<i>-I'm in Miami too.</i>

1:05:29.625 --> 1:05:32.666
<i>I'm in contact with him,</i>
<i>and now with you.</i>

1:05:33.541 --> 1:05:35.000
<i>I came back to tell you.</i>

1:05:37.583 --> 1:05:40.416
<i>It's important that you understand:</i>

1:05:40.666 --> 1:05:41.666
<i>your safety,</i>

1:05:42.208 --> 1:05:43.625
<i>your husband's,</i>

1:05:44.083 --> 1:05:45.541
<i>your daughter's, mine,</i>

1:05:46.000 --> 1:05:47.250
<i>everyone's safety</i>

1:05:48.041 --> 1:05:50.375
<i>depends on you and your silence.</i>

1:05:52.250 --> 1:05:53.625
<i>You can trust me.</i>

1:05:58.666 --> 1:06:02.208
<i>[with emotion] My God!</i>
<i>All these years, I feel like...</i>

1:06:03.041 --> 1:06:03.875
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:06:05.125 --> 1:06:06.416
<i>Excuse me.</i>

1:06:09.875 --> 1:06:11.250
<i>All this...</i>

1:06:13.375 --> 1:06:17.583
<i>I need to take it in little by little,</i>
<i>not all at once.</i>

1:06:18.166 --> 1:06:19.000
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:06:35.416 --> 1:06:36.416
<i>[groans]</i>

1:06:52.041 --> 1:06:55.500
<i>[door opens and closes]</i>

1:07:03.666 --> 1:07:07.291
<i>[in English] I had an X-ray.</i>
<i>It's a sprain.</i>

1:07:07.916 --> 1:07:11.750
<i>-A bad one?</i>
<i>-No, they say it'll heal in two weeks.</i>

1:07:12.375 --> 1:07:13.208
<i>I'm good.</i>

1:07:14.416 --> 1:07:15.250
<i>I feel good.</i>

1:07:22.750 --> 1:07:23.583
<i>[scoffs]</i>

1:07:26.666 --> 1:07:28.000
<i>Can I ask you something?</i>

1:07:28.333 --> 1:07:30.833
<i>-Sure.</i>
<i>-Your closet is empty.</i>

1:07:32.208 --> 1:07:33.541
<i>Yes. The workers last week--</i>

1:07:33.625 --> 1:07:37.041
<i>Juan Pablo, I can't see your eyes.</i>
<i>Can you take your glasses off?</i>

1:07:38.875 --> 1:07:41.416
<i>-Mm-hmm.</i>
<i>-With the workers last week,</i>

1:07:42.041 --> 1:07:46.375
<i>all my clothes were covered with dust,</i>
<i>so I took it to the dry cleaners.</i>

1:07:46.791 --> 1:07:48.625
<i>I didn't want to bother you with it.</i>

1:07:49.083 --> 1:07:50.833
<i>That's very kind of you.</i>

1:07:57.666 --> 1:08:00.458
<i>-[sighs]</i>
<i>-I have to get up early tomorrow.</i>

1:08:01.000 --> 1:08:01.833
<i>At three.</i>

1:08:02.708 --> 1:08:03.583
<i>At three?</i>

1:08:04.166 --> 1:08:06.208
<i>Yeah, I ferry a boat to Freeport.</i>

1:08:07.666 --> 1:08:09.208
<i>I'll be gone for the weekend.</i>

1:08:12.041 --> 1:08:13.916
<i>[scoffs]</i>
<i>You have a bad arm.</i>

1:08:14.416 --> 1:08:15.625
<i>You still gonna go?</i>

1:08:16.166 --> 1:08:17.208
<i>[Roque, softly] Yes.</i>

1:08:19.000 --> 1:08:20.625
<i>What if I need to contact you?</i>

1:08:20.916 --> 1:08:22.625
<i>I'll keep my cellphone on.</i>

1:08:46.125 --> 1:08:50.125
<i>[mysterious tones playing]</i>

1:08:51.125 --> 1:08:52.166
<i>[Ana gasps]</i>

1:08:57.458 --> 1:08:58.333
<i>Remember?</i>

1:08:59.958 --> 1:09:01.291
<i>You're my bodyguard.</i>

1:09:03.000 --> 1:09:03.916
<i>[whispering] Yes.</i>

1:09:05.250 --> 1:09:06.583
<i>[softly] Your bodyguard.</i>

1:09:08.125 --> 1:09:09.333
<i>Like Kevin Costner.</i>

1:09:09.416 --> 1:09:12.333
<i>[both laugh]</i>

1:09:12.416 --> 1:09:13.250
<i>Look at me.</i>

1:09:13.333 --> 1:09:15.666
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

1:09:15.750 --> 1:09:17.583
<i>I will always protect you.</i>

1:09:19.958 --> 1:09:20.875
<i>[whispers] Always.</i>

1:09:22.708 --> 1:09:28.000
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

1:09:48.708 --> 1:09:50.708
<i>[tires squealing]</i>

1:09:54.500 --> 1:09:56.750
<i>[in Spanish] Damn! Ever the star!</i>

1:09:57.250 --> 1:10:00.666
<i>[Hernández] I'll help you!</i>

1:10:01.916 --> 1:10:03.375
<i>[Hernández in English] Hey, sir!</i>

1:10:03.458 --> 1:10:05.333
<i>[in Spanish] How did you do that?</i>

1:10:06.375 --> 1:10:07.958
<i>I slipped in the shower.</i>

1:10:08.875 --> 1:10:09.958
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

1:10:10.333 --> 1:10:11.708
<i>And you can't fly?</i>

1:10:12.458 --> 1:10:14.666
<i>No... not with a brace.</i>

1:10:15.125 --> 1:10:15.958
<i>Hmm.</i>

1:10:18.250 --> 1:10:20.416
<i>We had to reorganize at the last minute.</i>

1:10:22.291 --> 1:10:25.000
<i>[slapping on backs]</i>

1:10:28.541 --> 1:10:30.041
<i>Don't miss the plane.</i>

1:10:30.125 --> 1:10:35.583
<i>[PA in English] All areas </i>
<i>within the terminal building...</i>

1:10:36.125 --> 1:10:37.875
<i>[in Spanish] Your ticket to Havana.</i>

1:10:37.958 --> 1:10:40.291
<i>[mid-tempo rock music playing]</i>

1:10:43.958 --> 1:10:47.041
<i>[number dialing]</i>
<i>[line ringing]</i>

1:10:47.125 --> 1:10:49.375
<i>-[operator] </i>If you'd like to make a call--
<i>-[slams phone]</i>

1:10:55.625 --> 1:10:58.625
<i>[slamming charger and drawers]</i>

1:11:02.125 --> 1:11:03.208
<i>[door slams open]</i>

1:11:06.541 --> 1:11:07.708
<i>[Ana gasps]</i>

1:11:09.000 --> 1:11:10.833
<i>-[phone lands with force]</i>
<i>-[car door slams]</i>

1:11:10.916 --> 1:11:13.208
<i>[people shouting]</i>

1:11:20.500 --> 1:11:24.208
<i>[narrator in English] </i>In the fall of 1995,
more than 130 independent groups

1:11:24.291 --> 1:11:28.083
<i>joined forces,</i>
<i>calling</i> <i>themselves</i> <i>the</i> Concilio Cubano.

1:11:28.958 --> 1:11:33.041
<i>They announced three goals:</i>
<i>a peaceful transition to democracy,</i>

1:11:33.125 --> 1:11:35.375
<i>amnesty for political prisoners,</i>

1:11:35.458 --> 1:11:39.375
<i>and participation by Cuban exiles </i>
<i>in the transition to democracy.</i>

1:11:40.125 --> 1:11:41.833
<i>The reprisal was brutal.</i>

1:11:42.750 --> 1:11:46.791
<i>The Castro regime attacked </i>Concilio<i> </i>Cubano
<i>with all of its strength.</i>

1:11:46.875 --> 1:11:49.041
<i>In February, they went all out.</i>

1:11:49.125 --> 1:11:50.666
<i>They ransacked homes.</i>

1:11:50.750 --> 1:11:52.291
<i>They attacked people.</i>

1:11:52.375 --> 1:11:55.833
<i>They imprisoned hundreds</i>
<i>of human rights activists.</i>

1:11:55.916 --> 1:11:57.916
<i>People who didn't have weapons.</i>

1:11:58.000 --> 1:12:02.041
<i>People who only aspired</i>
<i>to gather peacefully in La Havana.</i>

1:12:02.625 --> 1:12:03.541
<i>[man] Mr. Basulto!</i>

1:12:03.625 --> 1:12:05.208
<i>[cameras clicking]</i>

1:12:05.291 --> 1:12:07.833
<i>[reporter] Do you have anything to say</i>
<i>about the situation in Cuba?</i>

1:12:07.916 --> 1:12:11.250
<i>Well, we don't have much information,</i>

1:12:11.333 --> 1:12:15.250
<i>but this is obviously the reaction</i>
<i>of the government on its last legs,</i>

1:12:15.333 --> 1:12:19.000
<i>and proof of the strength</i>
<i>of the democratic movement.</i>

1:12:19.583 --> 1:12:24.958
<i>For all Cubans craving freedom,</i>
<i>the hour of truth has arrived.</i>

1:12:25.833 --> 1:12:29.916
<i>Today</i> Hermano<i> will drop flyers</i>

1:12:30.000 --> 1:12:34.166
<i>over</i> <i>Havana</i>
<i>in</i> <i>support of the</i> Concilio Cubano.

1:12:34.666 --> 1:12:36.875
<i>[in Spanish] Give us our course,</i>

1:12:37.625 --> 1:12:38.916
<i>our direction...</i>

1:12:39.500 --> 1:12:43.000
<i>[all] Give us our course, our direction...</i>

1:12:43.083 --> 1:12:45.166
<i>and guide our planes</i>

1:12:45.250 --> 1:12:48.541
<i>to our brothers on the sea.</i>

1:12:48.958 --> 1:12:53.708
<i>[all] and guide our planes</i>
<i>to our brothers on the sea.</i>

1:12:54.625 --> 1:12:55.458
<i>[Basulto] Good luck.</i>

1:12:55.541 --> 1:12:56.708
<i>Good luck, everyone.</i>

1:12:56.791 --> 1:12:59.875
<i>[applause]</i>

1:13:16.000 --> 1:13:22.958
<i>[moody music playing]</i>

1:13:47.333 --> 1:13:51.791
<i>[Basulto in English] </i>Good afternoon,
Havana Center. This is November 2-5-0-6,

1:13:51.875 --> 1:13:54.458
<i>crossing the 24th Parallel.</i>

1:13:54.541 --> 1:14:00.166
<i>Today our area of operation will be</i>
<i>the region north of Havana.</i>

1:14:00.250 --> 1:14:02.791
<i>[air traffic control] </i>Good afternoon,
November 2-5-0-6.

1:14:02.875 --> 1:14:06.583
<i>Airspace to the north of the city</i>
<i>is restricted airspace.</i>

1:14:06.666 --> 1:14:12.000
<i>If you cross the 24th Parallel,</i>
<i>you're putting yourself in great danger.</i>

1:14:12.083 --> 1:14:16.333
<i>We know we are in danger</i>
<i>each time we cross south of 24.</i>

1:14:16.416 --> 1:14:21.833
<i>But we are ready to do it. As free Cubans,</i>
<i>we have the right to be here.</i>

1:14:34.916 --> 1:14:36.916
<i>[radio]</i> Reporting hostile movement
of Cuban fighter planes.

1:14:37.125 --> 1:14:40.291
<i>Hello Riverdale.</i>
<i>We have two planes ready for action,</i>

1:14:40.375 --> 1:14:42.750
<i>but superior orders forbid them</i>
<i>from taking off.</i>

1:14:42.833 --> 1:14:45.208
<i>I repeat:</i>
<i>we have express orders not to intervene.</i>

1:14:45.291 --> 1:14:48.750
<i>[radio in Spanish] Spirit of Miami,</i>

1:14:48.833 --> 1:14:51.083
<i>change your speed to 150.</i>

1:14:51.166 --> 1:14:53.041
<i>Here's </i>Spirit of Miami.

1:14:53.125 --> 1:14:54.333
<i>Changing to 150.</i>

1:15:00.125 --> 1:15:02.250
<i>[radio]</i> 4-6-8 what is your altitude?

1:15:02.333 --> 1:15:05.125
<i>1,700 meters. Three planes in sight.</i>

1:15:05.208 --> 1:15:06.541
<i>Switch on your radars.</i>

1:15:06.708 --> 1:15:09.916
<i>Copy that.</i>
<i>Target locked. It's a private plane.</i>

1:15:11.375 --> 1:15:13.791
<i>[jet zooms past]</i>

1:15:15.000 --> 1:15:16.500
<i>We've got company.</i>

1:15:17.125 --> 1:15:19.083
<i>Enemy MiGs flying around us.</i>

1:15:19.583 --> 1:15:20.750
<i>[radio] </i>There's no risk.

1:15:20.833 --> 1:15:22.708
<i>Just scare tactics!</i>

1:15:22.916 --> 1:15:28.416
<i>Permission to shoot.</i>
<i>Now or never! Permission, dammit.</i>

1:15:28.500 --> 1:15:31.375
<i>-Authorized.</i>
<i>-4-6-5, permission granted.</i>

1:15:31.458 --> 1:15:33.333
<i>[electronic tone]</i>

1:15:36.333 --> 1:15:37.416
<i>He vanished.</i>

1:15:37.500 --> 1:15:39.500
<i>[co-pilot] </i>Sure he's not behind us?

1:15:39.583 --> 1:15:42.000
<i>[missile blast]</i>

1:15:42.083 --> 1:15:43.125
<i>[explosive boom]</i>

1:15:43.583 --> 1:15:45.166
<i>[MiG pilot] </i>Got him!

1:15:47.000 --> 1:15:48.458
<i>Got the bastard!</i>

1:15:49.208 --> 1:15:52.125
<i>Seagull One? </i>Hear from <i>Spirit?</i>

1:15:52.500 --> 1:15:53.750
<i>Negative.</i>

1:15:54.416 --> 1:15:55.958
<i>See smoke on my left?</i>

1:15:56.041 --> 1:15:57.583
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:16:01.083 --> 1:16:02.416
<i>I see smoke!</i>

1:16:03.333 --> 1:16:05.041
<i>The two other Cessnas?</i>

1:16:05.250 --> 1:16:06.666
<i>Yes, still on course.</i>

1:16:07.916 --> 1:16:11.500
<i>[radio] </i>Stay in the zone at a low speed.

1:16:12.666 --> 1:16:14.291
<i>See the MiG?</i>

1:16:15.000 --> 1:16:15.875
<i>The MiG?</i>

1:16:15.958 --> 1:16:17.250
<i>Where the fuck is it?</i>

1:16:17.333 --> 1:16:18.500
<i>No...</i>

1:16:19.416 --> 1:16:20.625
<i>I see flames.</i>

1:16:20.708 --> 1:16:22.458
<i>Where are the flames?</i>

1:16:22.541 --> 1:16:24.083
<i>Damn it! Answer!</i>

1:16:25.875 --> 1:16:26.916
<i>Another plane ahead.</i>

1:16:27.000 --> 1:16:28.500
<i>Permission to shoot.</i>

1:16:28.583 --> 1:16:30.125
<i>Authorized.</i>

1:16:30.208 --> 1:16:32.000
<i>4-6-5. Permission to fire.</i>

1:16:32.083 --> 1:16:34.708
<i>Where the fuck is the MiG?</i>

1:16:35.750 --> 1:16:37.958
<i>[missile blasts]</i>

1:16:38.041 --> 1:16:39.125
<i>[explosive boom]</i>

1:16:39.583 --> 1:16:40.708
<i>Son of a bitch!</i>

1:16:41.041 --> 1:16:42.833
<i>[MiG pilot] </i>Destroyed!

1:16:43.375 --> 1:16:45.291
<i>Our country or death!</i>

1:16:45.666 --> 1:16:49.500
<i>They're fucking shooting!</i>

1:16:49.583 --> 1:16:51.041
<i>[dials beeping]</i>

1:16:53.791 --> 1:16:55.791
<i>[sound of phone ringing fades in]</i>

1:16:57.541 --> 1:16:59.750
<i>[ringing continues]</i>

1:17:00.250 --> 1:17:02.250
<i>-[Ana gasps]</i>
<i>-[phone rings again]</i>

1:17:02.375 --> 1:17:04.416
<i>-[in English] Hello?</i>
<i>-[man in Spanish] </i>Is Roque there?

1:17:04.500 --> 1:17:05.458
<i>Hi René!</i>

1:17:05.875 --> 1:17:09.583
<i>No, he left for the weekend.</i>
<i>He can't be reached.</i>

1:17:09.666 --> 1:17:11.208
<i>Is he with the Brothers?</i>

1:17:11.291 --> 1:17:14.125
<i>No, he broke his arm. He can't fly.</i>

1:17:14.208 --> 1:17:15.458
<i>Thank God!</i>

1:17:16.125 --> 1:17:17.416
<i>What's going on?</i>

1:17:18.000 --> 1:17:19.375
<i>Turn on your TV.</i>

1:17:25.041 --> 1:17:29.583
<i>[Basulto in English] </i>Something very tragic
that we have dreaded for a long time,

1:17:29.666 --> 1:17:31.958
<i>I believe happened today.</i>

1:17:32.041 --> 1:17:34.750
<i>I believe we lost our first pilots.</i>

1:17:34.833 --> 1:17:39.583
<i>These small airplanes were unarmed,</i>
<i>and clearly so.</i>

1:17:40.333 --> 1:17:42.875
<i>Cuban authorities knew that.</i>

1:17:42.958 --> 1:17:47.958
<i>The planes posed no credible threat</i>
<i>to Cuba’s security.</i>

1:17:48.041 --> 1:17:50.500
<i>[in Spanish]</i> I want to ask the world

1:17:50.583 --> 1:17:52.708
<i>which self-respecting country</i>

1:17:52.791 --> 1:17:54.333
<i>would be willing to accept,</i>

1:17:54.416 --> 1:17:56.625
<i>on its own territory,</i>

1:17:56.708 --> 1:17:59.666
<i>the major violations perpetrated</i>

1:17:59.750 --> 1:18:02.791
<i>against ours...</i>

1:18:13.083 --> 1:18:14.958
<i>[thumping]</i>

1:18:15.750 --> 1:18:19.666
<i>[voices murmuring]</i>

1:18:19.750 --> 1:18:21.750
<i>[clattering]</i>

1:18:34.416 --> 1:18:39.916
<i>[all] Look! Look, there she is!</i>
<i>Ms. Martínez!</i>

1:18:40.000 --> 1:18:42.416
<i>[knocking]</i>

1:18:43.541 --> 1:18:47.708
<i>...circumstances of how you left Cuba</i>
<i>and why you returned are rather murky.</i>

1:18:48.916 --> 1:18:52.333
<i>Sorry to ask you so bluntly, Mr. Roque,</i>

1:18:52.416 --> 1:18:55.000
<i>are you a spy for the Cuban government?</i>

1:18:55.083 --> 1:18:57.333
<i>I am not a State Security agent.</i>

1:18:58.250 --> 1:19:01.208
<i>I left Cuba for personal reasons,</i>
<i>my divorce. </i>

1:19:01.708 --> 1:19:03.750
<i>But why did I decide to return?</i>

1:19:04.208 --> 1:19:07.125
<i>I returned because I became frustrated</i>
<i>over there in the United States.</i>

1:19:07.208 --> 1:19:09.375
<i>I became frustrated with that society.</i>

1:19:09.458 --> 1:19:12.625
<i>I became frustrated</i>
<i>with the political intolerance</i>

1:19:12.708 --> 1:19:14.208
<i>in the emigrant community.</i>

1:19:15.750 --> 1:19:18.500
<i>I wasn't happy with the life I was living.</i>

1:19:19.166 --> 1:19:23.708
<i>I was deceived by militants,</i>
<i>claiming to be patriots,</i>

1:19:23.791 --> 1:19:26.375
<i>but who were in fact organizing</i>
<i>terrorist actions in Cuba</i>

1:19:26.458 --> 1:19:28.916
<i>while pretending to give humanitarian aid.</i>

1:19:29.833 --> 1:19:32.791
<i>They were told many times</i>
<i>not to violate Cuban airspace.</i>

1:19:32.875 --> 1:19:33.708
<i>Many times.</i>

1:19:34.666 --> 1:19:37.666
<i>And I said it to José Basulto.</i>
<i>You can ask him.</i>

1:19:39.166 --> 1:19:41.958
<i>“Basulto, this is crazy,</i>
<i>they’re gonna shoot down your planes."</i>

1:19:42.625 --> 1:19:45.250
<i>[reporter] </i>Can I end this
with a personal question?

1:19:46.125 --> 1:19:49.125
<i>What will you miss most</i>
<i>about your life in Miami?</i>

1:19:53.541 --> 1:19:55.041
<i>My Jeep Cherokee.</i>

1:19:56.500 --> 1:20:00.083
<i>[news theme plays]</i>

1:20:00.166 --> 1:20:02.166
<i>-[TV clicks off]</i>
<i>-[remote clatters]</i>

1:20:13.125 --> 1:20:14.416
<i>[in Spanish] Come on, Irma!</i>

1:20:14.958 --> 1:20:16.708
<i>Don't be greedy!</i>

1:20:17.541 --> 1:20:18.625
<i>Little girl...</i>

1:20:19.208 --> 1:20:20.625
<i>you're not in Cuba anymore.</i>

1:20:21.000 --> 1:20:22.666
<i>You don't have to save food.</i>

1:20:31.750 --> 1:20:32.708
<i>My girl!</i>

1:20:33.916 --> 1:20:35.250
<i>[kisses]</i>

1:20:38.000 --> 1:20:39.083
<i>You're different.</i>

1:20:39.166 --> 1:20:40.083
<i>Very?</i>

1:20:40.166 --> 1:20:41.583
<i>[laughs] Yes.</i>

1:20:42.458 --> 1:20:43.625
<i>[both laughing]</i>

1:20:45.166 --> 1:20:46.541
<i>Welcome.</i>

1:20:46.625 --> 1:20:48.375
<i>-My girl.</i>
<i>-[Irma] Dad.</i>

1:20:48.958 --> 1:20:51.666
<i>-[Olga] How are you?</i>
<i>-Good.</i>

1:20:53.583 --> 1:20:55.791
<i>My child, do you remember me?</i>

1:20:56.250 --> 1:20:58.916
<i>I'm your great-grandmother, Teté.</i>

1:20:59.458 --> 1:21:03.291
<i>[laughing] You were a baby</i>
<i>when I left Cuba.</i>

1:21:03.833 --> 1:21:07.916
<i>Look! This old lady is my sister Gladys.</i>

1:21:10.750 --> 1:21:12.916
<i>-[Irma] How are you?</i>
<i>-[Gladys] Good, and you?</i>

1:21:13.000 --> 1:21:14.958
<i>-[Irma] Good.</i>
<i>-[Gladys] Really good, no?</i>

1:21:24.083 --> 1:21:24.916
<i>[René sniffs]</i>

1:21:26.875 --> 1:21:28.208
<i>[René crying]</i>

1:21:31.000 --> 1:21:32.833
<i>[René sobs]</i>

1:21:36.708 --> 1:21:39.791
<i>Leave it. I'll do that.</i>

1:21:39.875 --> 1:21:43.041
<i>I'll say good night to Irma.</i>

1:21:50.625 --> 1:21:52.416
<i>You glad to be in Miami?</i>

1:21:53.083 --> 1:21:54.291
<i>I'm scared.</i>

1:22:00.250 --> 1:22:01.208
<i>Scared of what?</i>

1:22:02.625 --> 1:22:03.875
<i>I don't know.</i>

1:22:04.500 --> 1:22:05.666
<i>Of life.</i>

1:22:08.250 --> 1:22:09.416
<i>Life here?</i>

1:22:10.375 --> 1:22:11.541
<i>Everything's different.</i>

1:22:12.041 --> 1:22:12.875
<i>I know.</i>

1:22:14.875 --> 1:22:16.416
<i>Daddy's here.</i>

1:22:16.875 --> 1:22:18.583
<i>You have nothing to fear.</i>

1:22:27.416 --> 1:22:28.333
<i>Look.</i>

1:22:30.916 --> 1:22:32.250
<i>This photo of Fidel...</i>

1:22:36.875 --> 1:22:38.041
<i>Hide it.</i>

1:22:40.250 --> 1:22:42.208
<i>[Irma laughs]</i>

1:22:42.833 --> 1:22:43.750
<i>What is it?</i>

1:22:44.375 --> 1:22:46.333
<i>If you were really a traitor,</i>

1:22:46.416 --> 1:22:47.958
<i>you'd have torn it up.</i>

1:22:53.250 --> 1:22:54.416
<i>Sleep well.</i>

1:22:58.625 --> 1:23:00.041
<i>[Olga inhales deeply]</i>

1:23:05.625 --> 1:23:07.291
<i>[René] I have some friends</i>

1:23:08.458 --> 1:23:10.333
<i>who said they'd help us.</i>

1:23:10.791 --> 1:23:12.541
<i>They mentioned</i>

1:23:13.500 --> 1:23:16.041
<i>a job not far from here.</i>

1:23:16.125 --> 1:23:18.416
<i>In an old people's home.</i>

1:23:18.833 --> 1:23:21.916
<i>You'll have time to take care of Irma.</i>

1:23:25.791 --> 1:23:28.375
<i>It'll be hard to keep Irma out of this.</i>

1:23:28.875 --> 1:23:31.916
<i>Better to keep things as they are.</i>

1:23:32.250 --> 1:23:35.583
<i>You had no problem keeping me out of it.</i>

1:23:37.083 --> 1:23:38.750
<i>Will you forgive me?</i>

1:23:38.833 --> 1:23:40.208
<i>Truth is, I don't know.</i>

1:23:44.250 --> 1:23:45.208
<i>I understand you.</i>

1:23:45.291 --> 1:23:47.250
<i>And I, you.</i>

1:23:47.333 --> 1:23:51.208
<i>You did it for your country,</i>
<i>for our Revolution.</i>

1:23:51.875 --> 1:23:54.750
<i>I respect that. I even admire you.</i>

1:23:57.041 --> 1:23:58.541
<i>But the cost was high.</i>

1:23:58.625 --> 1:24:01.125
<i>For us, for your family.</i>

1:24:01.208 --> 1:24:03.833
<i>I don't know if you realize</i>
<i>what we went through.</i>

1:24:03.916 --> 1:24:07.125
<i>[gasps] For years I had a pain here</i>
<i>that wouldn't go away.</i>

1:24:08.208 --> 1:24:09.875
<i>I feel the same way.</i>

1:24:11.791 --> 1:24:14.041
<i>It won't be easy to forget.</i>

1:24:14.250 --> 1:24:18.041
<i>It's not the life I wanted</i>
<i>for my daughter and me.</i>

1:24:18.541 --> 1:24:19.708
<i>I'll make up for it--</i>

1:24:19.791 --> 1:24:22.958
<i>You made a decision</i>
<i>and we had to deal with it.</i>

1:24:25.375 --> 1:24:28.916
<i>Those wounds need time to heal.</i>

1:24:29.000 --> 1:24:31.791
<i>Remember how old Irma was</i>
<i>when you left?</i>

1:24:31.875 --> 1:24:33.833
<i>-[René] Come on--</i>
<i>-She was 6.</i>

1:24:33.916 --> 1:24:35.208
<i>Olga, please...</i>

1:24:38.125 --> 1:24:41.500
<i>Don't remind me how old she was</i>
<i>when I left Cuba.</i>

1:24:42.708 --> 1:24:45.833
<i>But remember it was your choice,</i>

1:24:45.916 --> 1:24:47.416
<i>not mine, not hers.</i>

1:24:50.333 --> 1:24:53.333
<i>I am here with you. In Miami.</i>

1:24:53.416 --> 1:24:57.375
<i>I never gave up on being your wife,</i>
<i>not even in Cuba.</i>

1:24:57.458 --> 1:25:01.750
<i>Being the wife of a traitor there</i>
<i>isn't easy.</i>

1:25:01.833 --> 1:25:05.625
<i>And I'm glad I made that choice.</i>

1:25:06.000 --> 1:25:09.166
<i>Why do you think</i>
<i>I trained in radio transmission?</i>

1:25:09.250 --> 1:25:10.708
<i>And all that other stuff.</i>

1:25:10.791 --> 1:25:13.750
<i>So I can help you! To be on your side.</i>

1:25:13.833 --> 1:25:18.041
<i>But don't expect it to happen overnight.</i>
<i>I need time.</i>

1:25:18.500 --> 1:25:21.791
<i>I need time, and so does our daughter.</i>

1:25:21.875 --> 1:25:23.000
<i>[sniffs]</i>

1:25:27.625 --> 1:25:30.208
<i>You have all the time in the world.</i>

1:25:32.416 --> 1:25:35.458
<i>As long as you give me reason to hope.</i>

1:25:37.125 --> 1:25:39.125
<i>[sighs, sniffs]</i>

1:25:41.250 --> 1:25:43.333
<i>-[Olga crying]</i>
<i>-[René]</i> <i>Shh.</i>

1:25:43.416 --> 1:25:44.625
<i>[René] Don't worry.</i>

1:25:45.583 --> 1:25:47.250
<i>We're together again.</i>

1:25:47.333 --> 1:25:49.041
<i>[Olga continues to cry]</i>

1:25:49.875 --> 1:25:55.250
<i>[melancholic music playing]</i>

1:25:56.375 --> 1:25:57.416
<i>[René] Can I hope?</i>

1:25:58.000 --> 1:26:00.000
<i>-[Olga] Of course.</i>
<i>-[radio static] </i>

1:26:00.083 --> 1:26:02.916
<i>[Olga] I've always loved you. Always.</i>

1:26:09.791 --> 1:26:12.291
<i>[in English] Please change</i>
<i>Mr. Barbeito’s bed. He soiled it.</i>

1:26:12.375 --> 1:26:13.291
<i>Yes, ma'am.</i>

1:26:15.416 --> 1:26:19.791
<i>[mysterious flute music playing]</i>

1:26:37.375 --> 1:26:38.833
<i>[retches]</i>

1:26:41.958 --> 1:26:43.750
<i>[man] You have many aliases:</i>

1:26:43.833 --> 1:26:47.000
<i>Solo, Ramón Medina, Basilio, Lupo.</i>

1:26:47.083 --> 1:26:48.500
<i>How should I refer to you?</i>

1:26:49.125 --> 1:26:52.000
<i>I am Luis Posada Carriles.</i>

1:26:52.416 --> 1:26:54.000
<i>You can use my real name.</i>

1:26:54.458 --> 1:26:57.791
<i>Mr. Posada Carriles,</i>
<i>how would you explain your relationship</i>

1:26:57.875 --> 1:27:00.041
<i>with the Cuban American</i>
<i>National Foundation?</i>

1:27:00.208 --> 1:27:04.791
<i>Jorge Mas Canosa, the chairman,</i>
<i>is a dear friend. </i>

1:27:05.166 --> 1:27:07.666
<i>And how would you define that friendship?</i>

1:27:07.750 --> 1:27:11.541
<i>Uh, we both love deep sea fishing.</i>

1:27:11.625 --> 1:27:14.083
<i>And he buys my paintings.</i>

1:27:14.166 --> 1:27:15.500
<i>Your paintings?</i>

1:27:15.583 --> 1:27:21.375
<i>Yes, I paint traditional Cuban landscapes.</i>
<i>It's how I make a living.</i>

1:27:21.458 --> 1:27:23.625
<i>These documents here,</i>

1:27:23.708 --> 1:27:27.291
<i>they show</i>
<i>some recent very important transfers</i>

1:27:27.375 --> 1:27:30.875
<i>from the Cuban American</i>
<i>National Foundation in New Jersey </i>

1:27:30.958 --> 1:27:33.583
<i>to a Salvadoran resident, Ramón Medina.</i>

1:27:33.666 --> 1:27:36.458
<i>Do you confirm</i>
<i>that Ramón Medina is one of your aliases?</i>

1:27:36.541 --> 1:27:38.416
<i>Yes, I do.</i>

1:27:38.500 --> 1:27:42.041
<i>And you deny these payments are associated</i>
<i>with terrorist activities?</i>

1:27:42.125 --> 1:27:46.416
<i>[laughs] Castro loves</i>
<i>to blame me for everything.</i>

1:27:46.500 --> 1:27:50.000
<i>[Posada Carriles] Do you know</i>
<i>what living in Cuba is like today?</i>

1:27:50.083 --> 1:27:51.208
<i>I do, I was there.</i>

1:27:51.666 --> 1:27:52.500
<i>It's communism.</i>

1:27:53.166 --> 1:27:54.833
<i>It's an economic failure.</i>

1:27:55.750 --> 1:27:58.083
<i>We are at war with communism.</i>

1:28:02.375 --> 1:28:04.291
<i>[in Spanish] Since Roque defected,</i>

1:28:04.875 --> 1:28:06.833
<i>Mas Canosa thinks there are more moles.</i>

1:28:10.291 --> 1:28:14.333
<i>It's become too dangerous for the CANF</i>
<i>to plan attacks on Cuba.</i>

1:28:15.666 --> 1:28:17.666
<i>They don't want to put the U.S. in a jam.</i>

1:28:18.666 --> 1:28:20.541
<i>So they have to keep...</i>

1:28:21.125 --> 1:28:22.375
<i>[in English] a low profile.</i>

1:28:24.166 --> 1:28:25.791
<i>[both in Spanish] Thank you.</i>

1:28:26.333 --> 1:28:27.958
<i>[René] They need a new strategy.</i>

1:28:29.375 --> 1:28:30.875
<i>To step up their ops.</i>

1:28:32.375 --> 1:28:34.333
<i>Can we implicate Mas Canosa?</i>

1:28:36.041 --> 1:28:37.375
<i>No smoking gun.</i>

1:28:38.833 --> 1:28:40.416
<i>They're very cautious.</i>

1:28:43.458 --> 1:28:45.416
<i>And guess who's in charge.</i>

1:28:46.875 --> 1:28:48.166
<i>Luis Posada Carriles.</i>

1:28:51.500 --> 1:28:53.416
<i>Posada Carriles, that motherfucker.</i>

1:28:55.208 --> 1:28:57.125
<i>They're recruiting in Central America.</i>

1:28:57.791 --> 1:28:59.958
<i>Nicaragua, El Salvador.</i>

1:29:01.000 --> 1:29:02.541
<i>They want mercenaries.</i>

1:29:04.083 --> 1:29:07.291
<i>Guys who'd kill their moms for a buck.</i>

1:29:18.166 --> 1:29:19.333
<i>[man] You need money?</i>

1:29:19.791 --> 1:29:20.916
<i>[man 2] I'm good.</i>

1:29:22.250 --> 1:29:24.541
<i>So why you selling your car?</i>

1:29:24.625 --> 1:29:26.541
<i>It's my sister's. We live together.</i>

1:29:26.625 --> 1:29:28.583
<i>One car is enough.</i>

1:29:30.583 --> 1:29:32.125
<i>If you need anything,</i>

1:29:32.666 --> 1:29:33.500
<i>just call.</i>

1:29:35.041 --> 1:29:37.666
<i>[gunshots]</i>

1:29:38.416 --> 1:29:39.333
<i>You know,</i>

1:29:40.041 --> 1:29:42.416
<i>I have friends who'd pay a man like you,</i>

1:29:42.833 --> 1:29:44.625
<i>reliable and brave.</i>

1:29:45.000 --> 1:29:46.250
<i>I don't touch drugs.</i>

1:29:46.625 --> 1:29:48.000
<i>This isn't about drugs.</i>

1:29:49.208 --> 1:29:50.625
<i>It's about planting a bomb.</i>

1:29:51.000 --> 1:29:51.833
<i>What for?</i>

1:29:52.291 --> 1:29:54.833
<i>No questions. It's part of the deal.</i>

1:30:00.208 --> 1:30:01.041
<i>[gunshot]</i>

1:30:02.583 --> 1:30:04.708
<i>I'll answer you once and for all.</i>

1:30:05.791 --> 1:30:07.666
<i>In 1989,</i>

1:30:07.750 --> 1:30:10.791
<i>Cuba produced 8 million tons</i>
<i>of cane sugar.</i>

1:30:11.208 --> 1:30:13.750
<i>Today... three million or less.</i>

1:30:14.125 --> 1:30:17.333
<i>Without tourism,</i>
<i>their economy would plummet</i>

1:30:17.416 --> 1:30:19.416
<i>and the Castro regime would collapse.</i>

1:30:19.750 --> 1:30:21.541
<i>You have to hit where it hurts.</i>

1:30:21.708 --> 1:30:23.333
<i>Hotels, beaches.</i>

1:30:23.416 --> 1:30:24.625
<i>It's dangerous.</i>

1:30:25.916 --> 1:30:27.541
<i>15,000 Colones per bomb.</i>

1:30:28.416 --> 1:30:30.625
<i>And legal fees in case of trouble.</i>

1:30:33.000 --> 1:30:34.500
<i>-Welcome to Cuba.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

1:30:57.458 --> 1:30:58.333
<i>[puffing air]</i>

1:31:17.208 --> 1:31:19.208
<i>[jazzy music playing]</i>

1:31:19.291 --> 1:31:21.291
<i>[voices murmur]</i>

1:32:03.583 --> 1:32:07.166
<i>[plastic bag rustling]</i>
<i>[drops]</i>

1:32:13.083 --> 1:32:15.083
<i>-[birds chirp]</i>
<i>-[chatter]</i>

1:32:20.791 --> 1:32:22.791
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

1:32:38.708 --> 1:32:40.166
<i>[plastic bag rustling]</i>

1:32:52.625 --> 1:32:54.625
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

1:33:10.791 --> 1:33:12.791
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

1:33:17.041 --> 1:33:19.041
<i>[people talking]</i>

1:33:23.458 --> 1:33:26.333
<i>[ominous music intensifies]</i>

1:33:47.083 --> 1:33:53.416
<i>[rhythmic drum beats]</i>

1:33:54.083 --> 1:33:55.666
<i>Old Havana.</i>

1:33:55.958 --> 1:33:57.166
<i>[explosive echo]</i>

1:33:57.791 --> 1:33:59.208
<i>[in Italian] Sorry I'm late.</i>

1:33:59.291 --> 1:34:00.791
<i>My meeting just ended.</i>

1:34:00.875 --> 1:34:03.625
<i>We're enjoying our last day in Cuba.</i>

1:34:03.708 --> 1:34:05.666
<i>Tonight we'll be freezing in Toronto.</i>

1:34:05.750 --> 1:34:08.000
<i>Come, I booked a restaurant.</i>

1:34:10.875 --> 1:34:13.791
<i>[explosive boom]</i>

1:34:14.208 --> 1:34:16.208
<i>[people screaming]</i>

1:34:16.291 --> 1:34:18.083
<i>[crunching glass]</i>

1:34:18.166 --> 1:34:21.458
<i>[shouting and screaming continue]</i>

1:34:24.791 --> 1:34:26.458
<i>[explosion in distance]</i>

1:34:27.625 --> 1:34:28.958
<i>[in Spanish] What was that?</i>

1:34:29.041 --> 1:34:31.458
<i>Construction work at Hotel Panorama.</i>

1:34:32.291 --> 1:34:34.125
<i>Mind if I take off my T-shirt?</i>

1:34:34.208 --> 1:34:35.333
<i>[sirens wailing]</i>

1:34:35.416 --> 1:34:36.708
<i>Do as you please.</i>

1:34:37.125 --> 1:34:40.791
<i>Your pants too if you want.</i>
<i>You're the customer.</i>

1:34:44.875 --> 1:34:47.666
<i>-Why are we stuck?</i>
<i>-Roadblock.</i>

1:34:47.750 --> 1:34:49.416
<i>[siren]</i>

1:34:49.500 --> 1:34:50.708
<i>[bomber] Something happen?</i>

1:34:51.166 --> 1:34:53.166
<i>Must be Fidel going somewhere.</i>

1:34:54.083 --> 1:34:55.125
<i>[brakes whine]</i>

1:34:56.416 --> 1:34:58.583
<i>[motor approaching]</i>

1:35:00.500 --> 1:35:03.750
<i>They want us somewhere else!</i>

1:35:04.958 --> 1:35:05.916
<i>Let's go!</i>

1:35:06.083 --> 1:35:07.333
<i>[siren chirps]</i>

1:35:13.041 --> 1:35:16.125
<i>[salsa music playing]</i>

1:35:33.666 --> 1:35:34.541
<i>[retching]</i>

1:35:42.708 --> 1:35:43.791
<i>[bag drops]</i>

1:35:43.875 --> 1:35:46.375
<i>[sirens in distance]</i>

1:35:46.458 --> 1:35:49.250
<i>[eerie music playing]</i>

1:35:52.666 --> 1:35:53.833
<i>[sniffs]</i>

1:35:54.750 --> 1:35:57.166
<i>[sighing]</i>

1:35:58.333 --> 1:35:59.166
<i>[phone rings]</i>

1:36:01.583 --> 1:36:02.708
<i>[phone continues</i> <i>ringing]</i>

1:36:06.458 --> 1:36:08.708
<i>-Yes?</i>
<i>-[man] </i>Congratulations.

1:36:09.291 --> 1:36:11.541
<i>The attacks made the press.</i>

1:36:11.625 --> 1:36:13.583
<i>I told you I don't care.</i>

1:36:13.833 --> 1:36:16.791
<i>I need money. I can't even afford a taxi.</i>

1:36:16.958 --> 1:36:21.166
<i>Your money is in Havana.</i>
<i>An envelope at Hotel Capri.</i>

1:36:31.666 --> 1:36:33.708
<i>Wait here. I'll get the money.</i>

1:36:35.916 --> 1:36:39.125
<i>Raúl Ernesto Cruz León. That's my name.</i>

1:36:40.083 --> 1:36:42.208
<i>Nothing in that name, sir.</i>

1:36:42.291 --> 1:36:44.000
<i>An envelope?</i>

1:36:44.083 --> 1:36:46.625
<i>No, this is all I have.</i>

1:36:46.708 --> 1:36:48.791
<i>-Thank you.</i>
<i>-You're welcome.</i>

1:36:52.208 --> 1:36:55.166
<i>-[grunting]</i>
<i>-Don't try to resist!</i>

1:36:55.250 --> 1:36:56.958
<i>[squealing tires]</i>

1:36:57.541 --> 1:36:58.375
<i>[brakes screech]</i>

1:37:02.541 --> 1:37:04.083
<i>[engine revs]</i>

1:37:09.791 --> 1:37:12.291
<i>We saw you dumping this stuff</i>

1:37:12.375 --> 1:37:14.833
<i>in a trash can in Cervantes Park.</i>

1:37:15.708 --> 1:37:17.000
<i>Recognize it?</i>

1:37:17.958 --> 1:37:18.791
<i>No.</i>

1:37:19.958 --> 1:37:22.666
<i>[officer] The explosions</i>
<i>at the Tritón and Chateau hotels</i>

1:37:22.750 --> 1:37:26.291
<i>left only minor injuries</i>
<i>and material damage.</i>

1:37:26.958 --> 1:37:28.333
<i>But at the Copacabana,</i>

1:37:28.875 --> 1:37:32.916
<i>an Italian tourist had his throat slit</i>
<i>by a metal shard.</i>

1:37:35.291 --> 1:37:36.583
<i>He's dead.</i>

1:37:38.625 --> 1:37:40.125
<i>If you cooperate...</i>

1:37:42.041 --> 1:37:45.833
<i>you may be able to save your ass.</i>

1:37:47.666 --> 1:37:49.041
<i>Otherwise...</i>

1:37:50.583 --> 1:37:52.583
<i>it's the firing squad.</i>

1:37:53.000 --> 1:37:55.000
<i>[explosive boom]</i>

1:37:59.791 --> 1:38:01.500
<i>[horn honks]</i>

1:38:06.166 --> 1:38:08.166
<i>[uptempo music playing]</i>

1:38:09.208 --> 1:38:10.583
<i>[in English] Excuse me. Thank you.</i>

1:38:15.416 --> 1:38:16.625
<i>[Hernández in Spanish] Hey, man.</i>

1:38:17.541 --> 1:38:19.375
<i>-Olga?</i>
<i>-In the bathroom.</i>

1:38:19.916 --> 1:38:20.791
<i>So?</i>

1:38:21.875 --> 1:38:23.416
<i>You have news.</i>

1:38:24.291 --> 1:38:26.250
<i>Mas Canosa is very sick.</i>

1:38:27.416 --> 1:38:30.125
<i>-How sick?</i>
<i>-He won't last the year.</i>

1:38:34.291 --> 1:38:37.166
<i>They have a plan to kill Fidel.</i>
<i>It's in here.</i>

1:38:37.916 --> 1:38:39.166
<i>As always.</i>

1:38:39.875 --> 1:38:41.833
<i>Mas Canosa's last wish.</i>

1:38:42.250 --> 1:38:43.750
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:38:43.833 --> 1:38:45.833
<i>Last wish indeed.</i>

1:38:47.791 --> 1:38:51.583
<i>On Margarita Island, Venezuela.</i>
<i>The Ibero-American Summit.</i>

1:38:51.666 --> 1:38:55.208
<i>-That's very soon, barely a month away.</i>
<i>-[René] Yes.</i>

1:38:55.291 --> 1:38:59.791
<i>They have a boat, the </i>Esperanza,
<i>leaving from Puerto Rico.</i>

1:39:00.125 --> 1:39:01.041
<i>[steps approaching]</i>

1:39:03.708 --> 1:39:05.166
<i>-[in English] Thank you.</i>
<i>-[server] Okay.</i>

1:39:06.125 --> 1:39:08.958
<i>[in Spanish] Listen,</i>
<i>let's pass this on to the FBI.</i>

1:39:09.416 --> 1:39:10.375
<i>-The FBI?</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

1:39:13.291 --> 1:39:17.916
<i>Catch the CANF red-handed</i>
<i>and we score a major victory, man.</i>

1:39:22.000 --> 1:39:23.333
<i>Hello, Olga.</i>

1:39:23.416 --> 1:39:25.041
<i>-How are you?</i>
<i>-Good.</i>

1:39:25.875 --> 1:39:26.875
<i>Let's toast.</i>

1:39:27.875 --> 1:39:29.500
<i>To what?</i>

1:39:29.583 --> 1:39:31.291
<i>Cruz León's arrest.</i>

1:39:31.375 --> 1:39:34.333
<i>Four bombs. One dead tourist.</i>

1:39:35.375 --> 1:39:37.541
<i>-You feel responsible?</i>
<i>-Sure.</i>

1:39:37.958 --> 1:39:39.916
<i>We're here to stop that.</i>

1:39:40.416 --> 1:39:41.791
<i>We did what we can.</i>

1:39:41.875 --> 1:39:45.916
<i>We tracked them down,</i>
<i>dismantled their organization.</i>

1:39:46.333 --> 1:39:48.125
<i>The recruiter is on the run now.</i>

1:39:48.208 --> 1:39:50.833
<i>But we have reasons to celebrate.</i>

1:39:50.916 --> 1:39:51.750
<i>Indeed.</i>

1:39:52.458 --> 1:39:55.041
<i>We have some good news for you.</i>

1:39:56.250 --> 1:39:57.625
<i>What's happening?</i>

1:39:58.750 --> 1:39:59.791
<i>I'm pregnant!</i>

1:39:59.875 --> 1:40:01.500
<i>-[René laughs]</i>
<i>-[Hernández gasps]</i>

1:40:01.583 --> 1:40:02.458
<i>Yes.</i>

1:40:02.833 --> 1:40:05.541
<i>We waited to tell you until we were sure.</i>

1:40:05.625 --> 1:40:07.375
<i>Now we are.</i>

1:40:07.458 --> 1:40:09.250
<i>I had an ultrasound.</i>

1:40:09.333 --> 1:40:11.750
<i>Everything's fine. It's a girl.</i>

1:40:11.833 --> 1:40:13.791
<i>Congratulations! Great news.</i>

1:40:13.875 --> 1:40:15.333
<i>-[René] Thank you.</i>
<i>-Got a name yet?</i>

1:40:15.416 --> 1:40:18.083
<i>-[René] Yes, Ivett.</i>
<i>-[all] Ivett.</i>

1:40:18.166 --> 1:40:20.666
<i>-Pretty, isn't it?</i>
<i>-Yes, very.</i>

1:40:20.750 --> 1:40:22.208
<i>Ivett... I like it.</i>

1:40:22.500 --> 1:40:24.833
<i>-How is Irma doing?</i>
<i>-[René] Fine.</i>

1:40:24.916 --> 1:40:27.250
<i>She speaks fluent English.</i>

1:40:27.750 --> 1:40:30.333
<i>-Irma is jealous, of course.</i>
<i>-Hmm.</i>

1:40:30.416 --> 1:40:32.166
<i>But she'll get over it.</i>

1:40:33.583 --> 1:40:37.291
<i>We all have to. Just watch out.</i>

1:40:37.375 --> 1:40:39.375
<i>I know, poor thing.</i>

1:40:39.458 --> 1:40:41.250
<i>But there's no other remedy</i>

1:40:41.333 --> 1:40:43.250
<i>but to learn she's not the center.</i>

1:40:44.083 --> 1:40:48.125
<i>[radio in English]</i> <i>Esperanza</i> for <i>Baranof.</i>
This is <i>US Coast Guard Cutter Baranof.</i>

1:40:48.750 --> 1:40:50.750
<i>Please state your purpose</i>
<i>in these waters.</i>

1:40:51.625 --> 1:40:54.416
<i>Esperanza</i> to <i>Baranof. </i>We're tourists.

1:40:54.500 --> 1:40:55.833
<i>We're on a fishing trip.</i>

1:40:55.916 --> 1:40:59.208
<i>[siren wailing]</i>

1:41:04.625 --> 1:41:05.541
<i>Final destination?</i>

1:41:05.625 --> 1:41:06.666
<i>Santa Lucia.</i>

1:41:07.916 --> 1:41:09.000
<i>[from cabin] Down here.</i>

1:41:17.041 --> 1:41:18.541
<i>[officer] Is this your fishing gear?</i>

1:41:18.625 --> 1:41:20.416
<i>Those weapons are mine.</i>
<i>My passengers had no idea--</i>

1:41:20.500 --> 1:41:22.166
<i>[officer] Anything you say</i>
<i>may be held against you.</i>

1:41:22.250 --> 1:41:25.416
<i>They are to be used to kill Fidel Castro.</i>
<i>And I am proud of it.</i>

1:41:27.750 --> 1:41:30.125
<i>[man] </i>President Castro gave me a message

1:41:30.208 --> 1:41:32.833
<i>to be delivered to President Clinton</i>
<i>in person.</i>

1:41:34.708 --> 1:41:36.500
<i>The president will be informed.</i>

1:41:37.083 --> 1:41:41.000
<i>Cuban intelligence have been gathering</i>
<i>overwhelming information</i>

1:41:41.083 --> 1:41:42.375
<i>for several years now.</i>

1:41:42.458 --> 1:41:45.833
<i>We keep a close eye</i>
<i>on Cuban exile organizations.</i>

1:41:45.916 --> 1:41:48.916
<i>Then you know</i>
<i>that the CANF is financing terrorists</i>

1:41:49.000 --> 1:41:52.416
<i>and that the operations</i>
<i>are carried on by mercenaries</i>

1:41:52.500 --> 1:41:54.500
<i>recruited in Central America.</i>

1:41:54.583 --> 1:41:56.875
<i>Is Cuba willing to share its intel?</i>

1:41:56.958 --> 1:42:00.166
<i>I'm sure</i>
<i>if you approach the Cuban authorities,</i>

1:42:00.250 --> 1:42:02.208
<i>they will respond positively.</i>

1:42:18.083 --> 1:42:20.583
<i>In front of you,</i>
<i>you will find three files.</i>

1:42:21.000 --> 1:42:24.708
<i>The first,</i>
<i>is the report on terrorist activities</i>

1:42:24.791 --> 1:42:26.791
<i>against Cuba since 1990.</i>

1:42:28.166 --> 1:42:32.166
<i>You will find proof that most operations</i>
<i>led by other groups,</i>

1:42:32.250 --> 1:42:34.291
<i>were, in fact, commissioned by the CANF.</i>

1:42:35.083 --> 1:42:37.750
<i>In the second, you have a list</i>

1:42:37.833 --> 1:42:41.541
<i>of 40 Cuban exiles</i>
<i>identified as active terrorists.</i>

1:42:41.875 --> 1:42:46.166
<i>And in the third, money wired by the CANF</i>

1:42:46.250 --> 1:42:51.458
<i>to terrorist Luis Posada Carriles,</i>
<i>establishing his connection to CANF.</i>

1:42:51.875 --> 1:42:53.541
<i>Those are your conclusions?</i>

1:43:00.791 --> 1:43:02.750
<i>All the facts are here</i>

1:43:03.750 --> 1:43:05.791
<i>at your disposal.</i>

1:43:06.791 --> 1:43:10.583
<i>[in Spanish] You think</i>
<i>the heads of the CANF will be affected</i>

1:43:10.666 --> 1:43:13.916
<i>by the Cuban intel given to the FBI?</i>

1:43:14.375 --> 1:43:15.875
<i>Well...</i>

1:43:16.375 --> 1:43:19.708
<i>Mas Canosa is not around anymore.</i>
<i>He passed.</i>

1:43:21.500 --> 1:43:25.250
<i>He always said</i>
<i>he didn't want to know of my activities.</i>

1:43:25.500 --> 1:43:29.583
<i>[sighs] I don't think the CANF</i>

1:43:30.291 --> 1:43:31.750
<i>will be upset.</i>

1:43:32.875 --> 1:43:35.083
<i>But the communist Cubans</i>

1:43:35.750 --> 1:43:39.875
<i>have a lot to worry about.</i>

1:43:39.958 --> 1:43:41.583
<i>Why would you say that?</i>

1:43:42.166 --> 1:43:43.375
<i>Do the math.</i>

1:43:43.916 --> 1:43:46.291
<i>Where does Cuban intel come from?</i>

1:43:46.708 --> 1:43:50.791
<i>A Cuban spy ring in Miami.</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:43:50.875 --> 1:43:52.250
<i>Honestly...</i>

1:43:52.708 --> 1:43:57.583
<i>[sighs] you think the FBI</i>
<i>can tolerate such activities</i>

1:43:57.666 --> 1:43:59.916
<i>on American soil?</i>

1:44:01.291 --> 1:44:02.791
<i>I highly doubt it.</i>

1:44:02.875 --> 1:44:05.458
<i>[laughing] I highly doubt it.</i>

1:44:06.000 --> 1:44:07.208
<i>[phone rings]</i>

1:44:07.291 --> 1:44:08.250
<i>[Olga] </i>Good afternoon.

1:44:08.333 --> 1:44:11.041
<i>[in English] </i>I'm Olga Salanueva
from <i>Ingles Ahora.</i>

1:44:11.125 --> 1:44:16.000
<i>We are offering to perfect your English</i>
<i>in order to assimilate better into so--</i>

1:44:16.541 --> 1:44:17.541
<i>[in Spanish] Fine.</i>

1:44:18.041 --> 1:44:20.958
<i>Yes, yes. Some other time.</i>
<i>Sorry to bother you.</i>

1:44:21.041 --> 1:44:22.500
<i>Thank you very much.</i>

1:44:24.750 --> 1:44:27.625
<i>[man in English] Olga!</i>
<i>Where are you going?</i>

1:44:28.500 --> 1:44:30.250
<i>To pick up my daughter at daycare.</i>

1:44:30.333 --> 1:44:33.291
<i>But it's not time to leave.</i>
<i>I told you to figure something out.</i>

1:44:33.375 --> 1:44:35.666
<i>I know, but the school is far. I'm sorry.</i>

1:44:35.750 --> 1:44:37.750
<i>["Western Union" playing]</i>

1:44:39.791 --> 1:44:41.500
<i>-[in Spanish] How's it going?</i>
<i>-Great.</i>

1:44:41.583 --> 1:44:43.708
<i>-How about your exam?</i>
<i>-9/10.</i>

1:44:44.708 --> 1:44:45.958
<i>[René] Hey, honey.</i>

1:44:46.041 --> 1:44:50.000
<i>Here on Friday?</i>
<i>No </i>Movimiento Democracia <i>meeting?</i>

1:44:50.083 --> 1:44:52.375
<i>[René] It's next week instead.</i>

1:44:52.458 --> 1:44:53.791
<i>Great.</i>

1:44:53.875 --> 1:44:56.916
<i>[René] So I'm home. Enjoying a rest.</i>

1:44:57.791 --> 1:44:58.625
<i>[René] What about you?</i>

1:44:58.708 --> 1:45:02.416
<i>[Olga] Can you change her?</i>
<i>I smell something off.</i>

1:45:02.500 --> 1:45:03.916
<i>Something off?</i>

1:45:04.000 --> 1:45:06.458
<i>What did you do?</i>

1:45:07.041 --> 1:45:08.291
<i>[Irma] I'll help.</i>

1:45:13.333 --> 1:45:15.500
<i>[René] That's why you're crying.</i>

1:45:15.916 --> 1:45:17.916
<i>[René shushes the baby]</i>

1:45:30.708 --> 1:45:33.916
<i>[René speaking softly]</i>

1:45:34.000 --> 1:45:36.875
<i>[René in English] ...proposed.</i>
<i>Combined...</i>

1:45:36.958 --> 1:45:41.333
<i>[René and Irma speaking in Spanish]</i>

1:45:41.416 --> 1:45:43.000
<i>[Olga] Look at me!</i>

1:45:43.416 --> 1:45:44.416
<i>What?</i>

1:45:44.833 --> 1:45:46.833
<i>[Olga] Nice light. I want a picture.</i>

1:45:46.916 --> 1:45:48.708
<i>In my underwear?</i>

1:45:48.791 --> 1:45:52.083
<i>[Olga] Closer. I want the three of you.</i>

1:45:52.166 --> 1:45:55.708
<i>[all speaking in Spanish]</i>

1:45:55.791 --> 1:45:58.000
<i>Look at the camera!</i>

1:45:58.083 --> 1:46:00.083
<i>[Olga cooing]</i>

1:46:01.583 --> 1:46:03.875
<i>-[Olga cooing again]</i>
<i>-[shutter clicks]</i>

1:46:05.708 --> 1:46:08.416
<i>[baby fussing]</i>

1:46:08.500 --> 1:46:12.166
<i>[baby cries]</i>

1:46:15.833 --> 1:46:19.000
<i>[crying grows louder]</i>

1:46:28.833 --> 1:46:33.208
<i>[baby whimpering]</i>

1:46:41.583 --> 1:46:45.166
<i>[helicopter in the distance]</i>

1:46:48.833 --> 1:46:53.416
<i>[helicopter draws closer]</i>

1:46:55.791 --> 1:46:58.583
<i>[helicopter very close]</i>

1:46:58.666 --> 1:47:00.291
<i>-[door crashes]</i>
<i>-[footsteps]</i>

1:47:00.375 --> 1:47:02.666
<i>[agent in English] Move to the right!</i>
<i>Pick up the left!</i>

1:47:03.708 --> 1:47:04.583
<i>[heavy thud]</i>

1:47:04.666 --> 1:47:06.458
<i>-[agent] Clear!</i>
<i>-Show me your hands!</i>

1:47:06.541 --> 1:47:08.125
<i>On your knees!</i>

1:47:08.208 --> 1:47:10.833
<i>[agent 2] You're under arrest</i>
<i>for spying on the United States of--</i>

1:47:10.916 --> 1:47:13.083
<i>-[shouting]</i>
<i>-[female agent] Come here!</i>

1:47:13.166 --> 1:47:15.166
<i>[agent 2] Get that kid out of here!</i>

1:47:16.208 --> 1:47:18.208
<i>You have the right to remain silent.</i>

1:47:18.291 --> 1:47:19.666
<i>Anything you say, can and will...</i>

1:47:19.750 --> 1:47:21.375
<i>-[agent] Don't move!</i>
<i>-[baby screaming]</i>

1:47:21.458 --> 1:47:24.416
<i>-Papa!</i>
<i>-Calm down!</i>

1:47:24.500 --> 1:47:27.583
<i>Irma! Don't touch my daughter!</i>

1:47:29.500 --> 1:47:30.875
<i>[agent] You have the right</i>
<i>to remain silent.</i>

1:47:30.958 --> 1:47:34.583
<i>Anything you say, can and will be used</i>
<i>against you in the court of law.</i>

1:47:34.666 --> 1:47:36.416
<i>You have the right to an attorney.</i>

1:47:36.500 --> 1:47:40.208
<i>If you cannot provide yourself with one,</i>
<i>one will be provided for you.</i>

1:47:40.291 --> 1:47:42.291
<i>Do you understand these rights</i>
<i>as I have read them?</i>

1:47:42.375 --> 1:47:43.541
<i>[in Spanish] Yes.</i>

1:47:49.250 --> 1:47:50.875
<i>[in Spanish] Olga, don't worry, my love.</i>

1:47:53.583 --> 1:47:57.291
<i>[baby wailing]</i>

1:47:57.375 --> 1:47:59.375
<i>[in English] Can I change</i>
<i>my daughter's diaper?</i>

1:48:01.125 --> 1:48:02.916
<i>[agent] Someone will come with you.</i>

1:48:08.333 --> 1:48:12.583
<i>[fading sirens]</i>

1:48:13.750 --> 1:48:16.541
<i>Your husband is an agent</i>
<i>in a Cuban spy ring.</i>

1:48:17.208 --> 1:48:20.041
<i>[agent] Not that I think</i>
<i>that that surprises you very much.</i>

1:48:20.125 --> 1:48:23.208
<i>Nine other agents</i>
<i>have been placed under arrest.</i>

1:48:23.916 --> 1:48:27.291
<i>We're here to ask you to collaborate</i>
<i>with the United States government.</i>

1:48:28.000 --> 1:48:31.958
<i>[agent 2] Your baby was born</i>
<i>in the United States. She's a citizen.</i>

1:48:32.041 --> 1:48:34.625
<i>This is not the case for you</i>
<i>and your older daughter.</i>

1:48:35.625 --> 1:48:37.958
<i>You understand that you can be deported</i>
<i>at any moment?</i>

1:48:38.625 --> 1:48:40.583
<i>I understand.</i>
<i>I want to talk to my husband.</i>

1:48:40.666 --> 1:48:42.666
<i>[agent 1] I can't let you do that.</i>

1:48:48.291 --> 1:48:53.708
<i>[chains jingling]</i>

1:49:21.291 --> 1:49:23.333
<i>-[bell rings]</i>
<i>-[bailiff] All rise.</i>

1:49:25.125 --> 1:49:27.500
<i>[bailiff] The Federal Court of Miami</i>
<i>is now in session.</i>

1:49:27.583 --> 1:49:30.041
<i>The Honorable Judge Lenard presiding.</i>

1:49:34.333 --> 1:49:38.083
<i>The United States against</i>
<i>Manuel Viramontez and associates.</i>

1:49:39.833 --> 1:49:43.541
<i>You are accused of conspiracy</i>
<i>to commit espionage,</i>

1:49:43.625 --> 1:49:47.500
<i>acting as foreign agents not registered</i>
<i>with the United States government,</i>

1:49:47.583 --> 1:49:49.500
<i>-falsifying documents...</i>
<i>-Daddy!</i>

1:49:49.583 --> 1:49:52.333
<i>...and perjury,</i>
<i>filling out immigration forms.</i>

1:49:52.416 --> 1:49:53.833
<i>[gavel pounds]</i>

1:49:56.333 --> 1:49:57.958
<i>[in Spanish] Such bad manners.</i>

1:49:58.041 --> 1:50:00.750
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-Nothing. Don't look.</i>

1:50:04.416 --> 1:50:08.000
<i>[squealing tires]</i>

1:50:08.083 --> 1:50:10.916
<i>[reporter] Excuse me,</i>
<i>do you know any of the accused?</i>

1:50:11.000 --> 1:50:15.125
<i>[reporters questioning]</i>

1:50:15.208 --> 1:50:16.500
<i>[reporter] Can you answer my question?</i>

1:50:16.583 --> 1:50:20.041
<i>[melancholic music playing]</i>

1:50:28.666 --> 1:50:31.083
<i>[in Spanish] Amarylis, it's me Olga.</i>

1:50:32.541 --> 1:50:34.250
<i>Good and you?</i>

1:50:34.625 --> 1:50:36.125
<i>Imagine here!</i>

1:50:36.458 --> 1:50:39.208
<i>I need a favor.</i>

1:50:40.125 --> 1:50:42.500
<i>Can you get Ivett to daycare?</i>

1:50:42.666 --> 1:50:45.583
<i>You have no idea of the circus here.</i>

1:50:52.500 --> 1:50:54.666
<i>[man in English] Olga,</i>
<i>can you follow me a moment please?</i>

1:50:54.750 --> 1:50:55.833
<i>Yes.</i>

1:50:56.958 --> 1:50:58.166
<i>Please, have a seat.</i>

1:51:01.083 --> 1:51:07.166
<i>[sighs] I guess you don't want to continue</i>
<i>to employ the wife of a Cuban spy.</i>

1:51:07.750 --> 1:51:10.958
<i>Look, as far as I know,</i>
<i>you haven't been convicted of anything.</i>

1:51:11.041 --> 1:51:12.666
<i>So for me, first and foremost,</i>

1:51:12.750 --> 1:51:14.875
<i>you're a mother</i>
<i>that has two children to feed.</i>

1:51:14.958 --> 1:51:19.166
<i>I've had my own problems with the FBI.</i>
<i>I know what scumbags those guys can be.</i>

1:51:19.500 --> 1:51:21.541
<i>So please, go back to work.</i>

1:51:25.333 --> 1:51:26.875
<i>[in Spanish] Please let me come.</i>

1:51:27.375 --> 1:51:31.250
<i>I'd love to. But you know you can't.</i>

1:51:31.791 --> 1:51:34.625
<i>And you must watch your sister.</i>

1:51:35.291 --> 1:51:38.208
<i>In this bag, milk, water and diapers.</i>

1:51:38.291 --> 1:51:39.958
<i>Tell Daddy I love him.</i>

1:51:40.583 --> 1:51:42.833
<i>Believe me, he'll be overjoyed.</i>

1:51:42.916 --> 1:51:44.708
<i>He sacrificed his family.</i>

1:51:44.791 --> 1:51:46.000
<i>Don't say that!</i>

1:51:46.500 --> 1:51:50.541
<i>Your father is brave,</i>
<i>guilty only of fighting for his country.</i>

1:51:50.625 --> 1:51:52.750
<i>-How about us?</i>
<i>-He does his duty.</i>

1:51:53.208 --> 1:51:54.875
<i>I wish he wasn't a soldier.</i>

1:51:54.958 --> 1:51:56.750
<i>I won't tell him that.</i>

1:52:01.166 --> 1:52:04.000
<i>I'll say his daughter is like him.</i>

1:52:04.750 --> 1:52:06.333
<i>Strong and courageous.</i>

1:52:07.416 --> 1:52:08.250
<i>Can I?</i>

1:52:09.541 --> 1:52:10.958
<i>Hey, can I?</i>

1:52:11.916 --> 1:52:12.791
<i>[kisses]</i>

1:52:13.833 --> 1:52:15.625
<i>[Olga] I'm getting by.</i>

1:52:15.708 --> 1:52:17.666
<i>I was able to keep my job.</i>

1:52:17.750 --> 1:52:18.666
<i>I'm glad.</i>

1:52:18.750 --> 1:52:21.041
<i>My boss is a good man.</i>

1:52:21.125 --> 1:52:22.875
<i>[laughs] </i>Who'd have thought?

1:52:23.500 --> 1:52:25.500
<i>[Olga inhales sharply]</i>

1:52:28.875 --> 1:52:29.708
<i>What?</i>

1:52:31.083 --> 1:52:34.208
<i>I'm trying to imagine your life in jail.</i>

1:52:36.250 --> 1:52:39.833
<i>I'm in a 6-by-12 foot cell.</i>

1:52:41.875 --> 1:52:45.916
<i>The only light comes</i>
<i>from a horizontal slat.</i>

1:52:47.125 --> 1:52:51.875
<i>20 inches long, 6 inches wide.</i>
<i>High up and out of reach.</i>

1:52:53.583 --> 1:52:54.708
<i>That's my life.</i>

1:52:57.541 --> 1:53:00.708
<i>And the girls?</i>
<i>How are they dealing with it?</i>

1:53:00.791 --> 1:53:03.416
<i>It's tough, especially for Irma.</i>

1:53:03.833 --> 1:53:05.166
<i>But we're okay.</i>

1:53:10.625 --> 1:53:12.208
<i>The FBI offered me a plea deal.</i>

1:53:13.541 --> 1:53:15.333
<i>What does that mean?</i>

1:53:16.583 --> 1:53:18.833
<i>Informing for a reduced sentence.</i>

1:53:22.291 --> 1:53:23.125
<i>And?</i>

1:53:23.708 --> 1:53:26.333
<i>Five of the others agreed to it.</i>

1:53:26.666 --> 1:53:27.916
<i>They'll speak?</i>

1:53:30.625 --> 1:53:33.208
<i>You won't cooperate, will you?</i>

1:53:36.708 --> 1:53:39.416
<i>You and the girls will be deported</i>
<i>if I don't.</i>

1:53:42.541 --> 1:53:45.166
<i>[woman] </i>Mr. President, as you know,

1:53:45.250 --> 1:53:48.708
<i>10 Cuban Americans, of Cuban origin,</i>

1:53:48.791 --> 1:53:51.208
<i>were arrested and accused</i>

1:53:51.291 --> 1:53:54.541
<i>of spying for your government.</i>
<i>What can you say about this?</i>

1:53:54.625 --> 1:53:58.208
<i>What struck me, and we denounced it</i>

1:53:58.291 --> 1:53:59.916
<i>to the U.N.,</i>

1:54:00.000 --> 1:54:02.833
<i>was how amazing it was</i>

1:54:03.333 --> 1:54:07.250
<i>that the biggest spy in the world...</i>

1:54:08.291 --> 1:54:10.500
<i>would accuse of espionage</i>

1:54:10.708 --> 1:54:14.666
<i>the most spied upon country</i>
<i>in the world.</i>

1:54:15.250 --> 1:54:19.583
<i>Yes, we have sent Cuban citizens</i>

1:54:20.500 --> 1:54:22.375
<i>to infiltrate</i>

1:54:23.791 --> 1:54:26.458
<i>counter-revolutionary organizations.</i>

1:54:27.750 --> 1:54:29.416
<i>[Castro] </i>In order to report back

1:54:30.666 --> 1:54:33.500
<i>on activities of great interest to us.</i>

1:54:33.583 --> 1:54:36.208
<i>And I think we have the right to do so.</i>

1:54:36.708 --> 1:54:41.791
<i>As long as the U.S. tolerates</i>
<i>the organization of sabotage,</i>

1:54:42.125 --> 1:54:44.500
<i>armed incursions,</i>

1:54:44.833 --> 1:54:49.833
<i>attacks of tourist facilities,</i>

1:54:50.958 --> 1:54:54.625
<i>smuggling weapons and explosives,</i>

1:54:54.708 --> 1:54:58.541
<i>and attacks on our economy,</i>
<i>our tourism industry.</i>

1:54:58.625 --> 1:55:02.041
<i>All these things which we have denounced.</i>

1:55:03.125 --> 1:55:05.041
<i>[doors slamming]</i>

1:55:05.125 --> 1:55:07.291
<i>[metal detector beeping]</i>

1:55:11.916 --> 1:55:13.791
<i>[metal detector whining]</i>

1:55:13.875 --> 1:55:15.875
<i>[keys jangling]</i>

1:55:15.958 --> 1:55:20.541
<i>-[lock clicks open]</i>
<i>-[buzzer sounds]</i>

1:55:30.083 --> 1:55:31.833
<i>[baby giggling]</i>

1:55:31.916 --> 1:55:33.333
<i>Little darling...</i>

1:55:33.416 --> 1:55:36.333
<i>[Irma] Give a kiss to Daddy,</i>
<i>give him a kiss.</i>

1:55:36.750 --> 1:55:39.708
<i>-[René kisses glass]</i>
<i>-[baby cooing]</i>

1:55:40.166 --> 1:55:45.416
<i>[René speaking indistinctly]</i>

1:55:45.500 --> 1:55:48.375
<i>-[Olga] </i>Show him your duck.
<i>-[René] My love.</i>

1:55:48.458 --> 1:55:51.666
<i>[baby laughing]</i>

1:55:54.416 --> 1:55:56.625
<i>[René] Ducky fell again?</i>

1:55:56.708 --> 1:55:59.333
<i>Another kiss.</i>
<i>[kisses]</i>

1:56:00.208 --> 1:56:02.833
<i>[kisses]</i>

1:56:05.875 --> 1:56:07.083
<i>[kisses]</i>

1:56:10.708 --> 1:56:13.708
<i>[baby babbling]</i>

1:56:13.791 --> 1:56:14.958
<i>She's a beauty.</i>

1:56:17.291 --> 1:56:19.375
<i>Prettier than her pictures.</i>

1:56:21.916 --> 1:56:26.166
<i>I brought you a package.</i>
<i>They need to check it first.</i>

1:56:27.000 --> 1:56:28.625
<i>I'll get it later.</i>

1:56:28.708 --> 1:56:30.750
<i>Mostly food and books.</i>

1:56:31.500 --> 1:56:33.291
<i>It's your birthday, remember?</i>

1:56:34.083 --> 1:56:34.958
<i>[René sighs]</i>

1:56:36.541 --> 1:56:38.333
<i>I'm sorry Irma isn't here.</i>

1:56:39.125 --> 1:56:41.208
<i>She's safer in Cuba.</i>

1:56:41.291 --> 1:56:42.166
<i>I know.</i>

1:56:42.250 --> 1:56:46.375
<i>She's with her Granny,</i>
<i>who takes good care of her.</i>

1:56:46.541 --> 1:56:48.458
<i>-You speak?</i>
-Every day.

1:56:48.541 --> 1:56:50.041
<i>School's going well?</i>

1:56:50.125 --> 1:56:53.000
<i>Yes. And she asks about you every day.</i>

1:56:56.041 --> 1:56:57.958
<i>I can't talk to her yet.</i>

1:57:00.166 --> 1:57:01.541
<i>It's too painful.</i>

1:57:04.375 --> 1:57:06.250
<i>Tell her Daddy loves her.</i>

1:57:06.333 --> 1:57:08.416
<i>I tell her that every day.</i>

1:57:08.791 --> 1:57:12.583
<i>When things get better,</i>
<i>we'll be together again.</i>

1:57:13.750 --> 1:57:14.750
<i>[sniffs]</i>

1:57:19.041 --> 1:57:20.833
<i>You know it won't be soon.</i>

1:57:25.500 --> 1:57:28.625
<i>You and Ivett will go to Cuba</i>
<i>to join Irma.</i>

1:57:30.166 --> 1:57:31.416
<i>Then what?</i>

1:57:34.041 --> 1:57:35.500
<i>I won't cooperate.</i>

1:57:37.291 --> 1:57:38.958
<i>I just told my lawyer.</i>

1:57:40.916 --> 1:57:43.250
<i>I can't testify against my brothers.</i>

1:57:44.250 --> 1:57:45.375
<i>I just can't.</i>

1:57:47.458 --> 1:57:50.791
<i>[whispering] </i>Even those
who testify against you?

1:57:50.875 --> 1:57:51.708
<i>No.</i>

1:57:52.291 --> 1:57:54.083
<i>Their morals aren't mine.</i>

1:57:58.208 --> 1:58:00.250
<i>Tell me if I have your support.</i>

1:58:00.750 --> 1:58:02.416
<i>Yes, you do.</i>

1:58:03.458 --> 1:58:06.833
<i>We'll be separated for a while.</i>
<i>You know that.</i>

1:58:13.375 --> 1:58:15.833
<i>I won't let you go through this alone.</i>

1:58:17.041 --> 1:58:20.416
<i>I'll visit you as often as they let me.</i>

1:58:20.500 --> 1:58:22.666
<i>I'll always be there for you.</i>

1:58:23.041 --> 1:58:24.708
<i>And for our daughters.</i>

1:58:25.583 --> 1:58:26.958
<i>I promise.</i>

1:58:36.041 --> 1:58:38.916
<i>[baby fussing]</i>

1:58:55.291 --> 1:58:57.208
<i>Sure you won't stay?</i>

1:58:57.375 --> 1:58:59.541
<i>I have to go.</i>

1:58:59.875 --> 1:59:01.750
<i>We must be prepared.</i>

1:59:01.833 --> 1:59:03.791
<i>[Teté] I understand.</i>

1:59:06.291 --> 1:59:09.166
<i>When things clear up,</i>
<i>I'll come back for her.</i>

1:59:09.250 --> 1:59:10.916
<i>And if they don't?</i>

1:59:11.375 --> 1:59:15.791
<i>Then she'll stay with you for a while.</i>

1:59:15.875 --> 1:59:18.625
<i>I know you'll tend to her</i>
<i>as if you were her mother.</i>

1:59:19.625 --> 1:59:20.541
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:59:23.666 --> 1:59:25.583
<i>Teté.</i>

1:59:25.666 --> 1:59:29.166
<i>Look at her, so tiny. And so sweet.</i>
<i>[crying]</i>

1:59:36.041 --> 1:59:39.625
<i>[Olga and baby babbling]</i>

1:59:41.791 --> 1:59:43.333
<i>Mama.</i>

1:59:44.125 --> 1:59:46.666
<i>-[kissing]</i>
<i>-[baby giggling]</i>

1:59:48.541 --> 1:59:51.291
<i>[Olga] We'll see each other soon.</i>
<i>Look at me.</i>

1:59:51.375 --> 1:59:52.666
<i>Look at Mommy.</i>

1:59:56.541 --> 2:00:02.291
<i>I love you.</i>

2:00:02.375 --> 2:00:05.375
<i>A little kiss.</i>
<i>[screams]</i>

2:00:09.208 --> 2:00:13.250
<i>[Olga continues baby talking]</i>

2:00:13.333 --> 2:00:15.708
<i>[Olga crying]</i>

2:00:15.791 --> 2:00:18.708
<i>[Teté] Come with Grandma.</i>

2:00:20.166 --> 2:00:21.750
<i>[both] Bye!</i>

2:00:21.833 --> 2:00:25.750
<i>See you soon!</i>

2:00:25.833 --> 2:00:27.458
<i>I love you.</i>

2:00:27.541 --> 2:00:29.250
<i>-I adore you.</i>
<i>-[Teté] Bye, Mommy!</i>

2:00:29.333 --> 2:00:30.708
<i>Thank you, Teté.</i>

2:00:30.791 --> 2:00:31.916
<i>I love you.</i>

2:00:32.000 --> 2:00:33.875
<i>-[Teté] Bye-bye, Mommy!</i>
<i>-[baby cooing]</i>

2:00:33.958 --> 2:00:35.791
<i>-[Teté] See you soon.</i>
<i>-[Olga sobbing]</i>

2:00:38.500 --> 2:00:40.791
<i>-[baby whimpering]</i>
<i>-[Teté baby talking]</i>

2:00:40.875 --> 2:00:44.458
<i>[car door slams]</i>
<i>[engine starts]</i>

2:00:46.333 --> 2:00:49.083
<i>[both] Mommy!</i>

2:00:49.166 --> 2:00:51.500
<i>[engine speeding off]</i>

2:00:51.583 --> 2:00:53.958
<i>[Teté speaking in Spanish]</i>

2:00:55.750 --> 2:00:57.083
<i>See you, Mommy!</i>

2:00:58.750 --> 2:01:00.625
<i>[both] Mommy.</i>

2:01:05.416 --> 2:01:08.416
<i>[man in English] Mrs. Salanueva?</i>
<i>We need you to come with us.</i>

2:01:09.916 --> 2:01:11.416
<i>Calm down, ma'am.</i>

2:01:16.791 --> 2:01:18.250
<i>[handcuffs click]</i>

2:01:18.333 --> 2:01:21.333
<i>[helicopter engine]</i>

2:01:27.833 --> 2:01:34.833
<i>["Asi te Amo" playing]</i>

2:05:29.916 --> 2:05:35.458
<i>[fades into a funky rock groove]</i>
